var book = {
	"name": "Matthew",
	"numChapters": 28,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23146A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23146A\"></sup>The book of the genealogy of Jesus Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23146B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23146B\"></sup>the son of David, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23146C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23146C\"></sup>the son of Abraham.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23147D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23147D\"></sup>Abraham was the father of Isaac, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23147E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23147E\"></sup>Isaac the father of Jacob, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23147F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23147F\"></sup>Jacob the father of Judah and his brothers,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23148G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23148G\"></sup>Judah the father of Perez and Zerah by Tamar, and Perez the father of Hezron, and Hezron the father of Ram,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and Ram the father of Amminadab, and Amminadab the father of Nahshon, and Nahshon the father of Salmon,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and Salmon the father of Boaz by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23150H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23150H\"></sup>Rahab, and Boaz the father of Obed by Ruth, and Obed the father of Jesse,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23151I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23151I\"></sup>Jesse the father of David the king.And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23151J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23151J\"></sup>David was the father of Solomon by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23151K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23151K\"></sup>the wife of Uriah,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23152L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23152L\"></sup>Solomon the father of Rehoboam, and Rehoboam the father of Abijah, and Abijah the father of Asaph,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and Asaph the father of Jehoshaphat, and Jehoshaphat the father of Joram, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23153M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23153M\"></sup>and Joram the father of Uzziah,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and Uzziah the father of Jotham, and Jotham the father of Ahaz, and Ahaz the father of Hezekiah,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and Hezekiah the father of Manasseh, and Manasseh the father of Amos, and Amos the father of Josiah,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23156N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23156N\"></sup>Josiah the father of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23156O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23156O\"></sup>Jechoniah and his brothers, at the time of the deportation to Babylon.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And after the deportation to Babylon: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23157P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23157P\"></sup>Jechoniah was the father of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23157Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23157Q\"></sup>Shealtiel, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23157R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23157R\"></sup>Shealtiel the father of Zerubbabel,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and Zerubbabel the father of Abiud, and Abiud the father of Eliakim, and Eliakim the father of Azor,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and Azor the father of Zadok, and Zadok the father of Achim, and Achim the father of Eliud,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and Eliud the father of Eleazar, and Eleazar the father of Matthan, and Matthan the father of Jacob,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and Jacob the father of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23161S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23161S\"></sup>Joseph the husband of Mary, of whom Jesus was born, who is called Christ.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So all the generations from Abraham to David were fourteen generations, and from David to the deportation to Babylon fourteen generations, and from the deportation to Babylon to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23162T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23162T\"></sup>the Christ fourteen generations.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now the birth of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23163U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23163U\"></sup>Jesus Christ took place in this way. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23163V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23163V\"></sup>When his mother Mary had been betrothed to Joseph, before they came together she was found to be with child <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23163W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23163W\"></sup>from the Holy Spirit.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And her husband Joseph, being a just man and unwilling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23164X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23164X\"></sup>to put her to shame, resolved to divorce her quietly.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But as he considered these things, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23165Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23165Y\"></sup>an angel of the Lord appeared to him in a dream, saying, “Joseph, son of David, do not fear to take Mary as your wife, for that which is conceived in her is from the Holy Spirit.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>She will bear a son, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23166Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23166Z\"></sup>you shall call his name Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23166AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23166AA\"></sup>for he will save his people from their sins.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23167AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23167AB\"></sup>All this took place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23167AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23167AC\"></sup>to fulfill what the Lord had spoken by the prophet:",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23168AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23168AD\"></sup>“Behold, the virgin shall conceive and bear a son,and they shall call his name <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23168AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23168AE\"></sup>Immanuel”(which means, God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23168AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23168AF\"></sup>with us).",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When Joseph woke from sleep, he did as the angel of the Lord commanded him: he took his wife,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>but knew her not until she had given birth to a son. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23170AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23170AG\"></sup>he called his name Jesus."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23171A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23171A\"></sup>after Jesus was born in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23171B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23171B\"></sup>Bethlehem of Judea <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23171C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23171C\"></sup>in the days of Herod the king, behold, wise men from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23171D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23171D\"></sup>the east came to Jerusalem,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>saying, “Where is he who has been born <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23172E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23172E\"></sup>king of the Jews? For we saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23172F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23172F\"></sup>his star when it rose and have come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23172G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23172G\"></sup>worship him.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When Herod the king heard this, he was troubled, and all Jerusalem with him;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and assembling all the chief priests and scribes of the people, he inquired of them where <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23174H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23174H\"></sup>the Christ was to be born.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They told him, “In Bethlehem of Judea, for so it is written by the prophet:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23176I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23176I\"></sup>“‘And you, O Bethlehem, in the land of Judah,are by no means least among the rulers of Judah;for from you shall come a rulerwho will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23176J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23176J\"></sup>shepherd my people Israel.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then Herod summoned the wise men secretly and ascertained from them what time the star had appeared.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And he sent them to Bethlehem, saying, “Go and search diligently for the child, and when you have found him, bring me word, that I too may come and worship him.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>After listening to the king, they went on their way. And behold, the star that they had seen when it rose went before them until it came to rest over the place where the child was.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When they saw the star, they rejoiced exceedingly with great joy.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And going into the house, they saw the child with Mary his mother, and they fell down and worshiped him. Then, opening their treasures, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23181K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23181K\"></sup>they offered him gifts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23181L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23181L\"></sup>gold and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23181M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23181M\"></sup>frankincense and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23181N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23181N\"></sup>myrrh.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23182O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23182O\"></sup>being warned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23182P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23182P\"></sup>in a dream not to return to Herod, they departed to their own country by another way.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now when they had departed, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23183Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23183Q\"></sup>an angel of the Lord appeared to Joseph in a dream and said, “Rise, take the child and his mother, and flee to Egypt, and remain there until I tell you, for Herod is about to search for the child, to destroy him.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And he rose and took the child and his mother by night and departed to Egypt",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and remained there until the death of Herod. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23185R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23185R\"></sup>This was to fulfill what the Lord had spoken by the prophet, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23185S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23185S\"></sup>“Out of Egypt I called my son.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then Herod, when he saw that he had been tricked by the wise men, became furious, and he sent and killed all the male children in Bethlehem and in all that region who were two years old or under, according to the time that he had ascertained from the wise men.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23187T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23187T\"></sup>Then was fulfilled what was spoken by the prophet Jeremiah:",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23188U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23188U\"></sup>“A voice was heard in Ramah,weeping and loud lamentation,Rachel weeping for her children;she refused to be comforted, because they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23188V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23188V\"></sup>are no more.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But when Herod died, behold, an angel of the Lord appeared in a dream to Joseph in Egypt,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>saying, “Rise, take the child and his mother and go to the land of Israel, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23190W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23190W\"></sup>those who sought the child's life are dead.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And he rose and took the child and his mother and went to the land of Israel.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But when he heard that Archelaus was reigning over Judea in place of his father Herod, he was afraid to go there, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23192X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23192X\"></sup>being warned in a dream he withdrew to the district of Galilee.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And he went and lived in a city called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23193Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23193Y\"></sup>Nazareth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23193Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23193Z\"></sup>so that what was spoken by the prophets might be fulfilled, that he would be called a Nazarene."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23194A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23194A\"></sup>In those days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23194B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23194B\"></sup>John the Baptist came preaching in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23194C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23194C\"></sup>the wilderness of Judea,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23195D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23195D\"></sup>“Repent, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23195E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23195E\"></sup>the kingdom of heaven is at hand.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For this is he who was spoken of by the prophet Isaiah when he said,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23196F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23196F\"></sup>“The voice of one crying in the wilderness:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23196G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23196G\"></sup>‘Prepare the way of the Lord;make his paths straight.’”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now John wore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23197H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23197H\"></sup>a garment of camel's hair and a leather belt around his waist, and his food was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23197I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23197I\"></sup>locusts and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23197J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23197J\"></sup>wild honey.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then Jerusalem and all Judea and all the region about the Jordan were going out to him,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and they were baptized by him in the river Jordan, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23199K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23199K\"></sup>confessing their sins.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But when he saw many of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23200L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23200L\"></sup>the Pharisees and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23200M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23200M\"></sup>Sadducees coming to his baptism, he said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23200N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23200N\"></sup>“You brood of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23200O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23200O\"></sup>vipers! Who warned you to flee from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23200P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23200P\"></sup>the wrath to come?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Bear fruit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23201Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23201Q\"></sup>in keeping with repentance.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And do not presume to say to yourselves, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23202R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23202R\"></sup>‘We have Abraham as our father,’ for I tell you, God is able from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23202S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23202S\"></sup>these stones to raise up children for Abraham.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Even now the axe is laid to the root of the trees. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23203T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23203T\"></sup>Every tree therefore that does not bear good fruit is cut down and thrown into the fire.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23204U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23204U\"></sup>“I baptize you with water <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23204V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23204V\"></sup>for repentance, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23204W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23204W\"></sup>he who is coming after me is mightier than I, whose sandals I am not worthy to carry. He will baptize you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23204X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23204X\"></sup>with the Holy Spirit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23204Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23204Y\"></sup>fire.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23205Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23205Z\"></sup>winnowing fork is in his hand, and he will clear his threshing floor and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23205AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23205AA\"></sup>gather his wheat into the barn, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23205AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23205AB\"></sup>but the chaff he will burn with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23205AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23205AC\"></sup>unquenchable fire.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23206AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23206AD\"></sup>Then Jesus came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23206AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23206AE\"></sup>from Galilee to the Jordan to John, to be baptized by him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23207AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23207AF\"></sup>John would have prevented him, saying, “I need to be baptized by you, and do you come to me?”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“Let it be so now, for thus it is fitting for us to fulfill all righteousness.”</span> Then he consented.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And when Jesus was baptized, immediately he went up from the water, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23209AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23209AG\"></sup>the heavens were opened to him, and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23209AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23209AH\"></sup>saw the Spirit of God descending like a dove and coming to rest on him;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23210AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23210AI\"></sup>a voice from heaven said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23210AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23210AJ\"></sup>“This is my beloved Son, with whom I am well pleased.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23211A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23211A\"></sup>Then Jesus was led up by the Spirit into the wilderness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23211B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23211B\"></sup>to be tempted by the devil.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And after fasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23212C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23212C\"></sup>forty days and forty nights, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23212D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23212D\"></sup>was hungry.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23213E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23213E\"></sup>the tempter came and said to him, “If you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23213F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23213F\"></sup>the Son of God, command <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23213G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23213G\"></sup>these stones to become loaves of bread.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But he answered, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23214H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23214H\"></sup>“It is written,</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23214I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23214I\"></sup>“‘Man shall not live by bread alone,</span><span class=\"woj\">but by every word that comes from the mouth of God.’”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23215J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23215J\"></sup>Then the devil took him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23215K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23215K\"></sup>the holy city and set him on the pinnacle of the temple",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and said to him, “If you are the Son of God, throw yourself down, for it is written,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23216L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23216L\"></sup>“‘He will command his angels concerning you,’and“‘On their hands they will bear you up,lest you strike your foot against a stone.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23217M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23217M\"></sup>it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23217N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23217N\"></sup>‘You shall not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23217O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23217O\"></sup>put the Lord your God to the test.’”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23218P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23218P\"></sup>Again, the devil took him to a very high mountain and showed him all the kingdoms of the world and their glory.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And he said to him, “All these I will give you, if you will fall down and worship me.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Be gone, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23220Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23220Q\"></sup>Satan! For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23220R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23220R\"></sup>it is written,</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23220S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23220S\"></sup>“‘You shall worship the Lord your God</span><span class=\"woj\">and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23220T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23220T\"></sup>him only shall you serve.’”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then the devil left him, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23221U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23221U\"></sup>angels came and were ministering to him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Now when he heard that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23222V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23222V\"></sup>John had been arrested, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23222W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23222W\"></sup>he withdrew into Galilee.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And leaving <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23223X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23223X\"></sup>Nazareth he went and lived in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23223Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23223Y\"></sup>Capernaum by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23223Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23223Z\"></sup>the sea, in the territory of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23223AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23223AA\"></sup>Zebulun and Naphtali,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23224AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23224AB\"></sup>so that what was spoken by the prophet Isaiah might be fulfilled:",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23225AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23225AC\"></sup>“The land of Zebulun and the land of Naphtali,the way of the sea, beyond the Jordan, Galilee of the Gentiles—",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23226AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23226AD\"></sup>the people dwelling in darknesshave seen a great light,and for those dwelling in the region and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23226AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23226AE\"></sup>shadow of death,on them a light has dawned.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23227AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23227AF\"></sup>From that time Jesus began to preach, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23227AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23227AG\"></sup>“Repent, for the kingdom of heaven is at hand.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23228AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23228AH\"></sup>While walking by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23228AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23228AI\"></sup>the Sea of Galilee, he saw two brothers, Simon (who is called Peter) and Andrew his brother, casting a net into the sea, for they were fishermen.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Follow me, and I will make you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23229AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23229AJ\"></sup>fishers of men.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Immediately they left their nets and followed him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And going on from there he saw two other brothers, James the son of Zebedee and John his brother, in the boat with Zebedee their father, mending their nets, and he called them.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Immediately they left the boat and their father and followed him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23233AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23233AK\"></sup>And he went throughout all Galilee, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23233AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23233AL\"></sup>teaching in their synagogues and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23233AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23233AM\"></sup>proclaiming the gospel of the kingdom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23233AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23233AN\"></sup>healing every disease and every affliction among the people.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So his fame spread throughout all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23234AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23234AO\"></sup>Syria, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23234AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23234AP\"></sup>they brought him all the sick, those afflicted with various diseases and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23234AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23234AQ\"></sup>pains, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23234AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23234AR\"></sup>those oppressed by demons, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23234AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23234AS\"></sup>those having seizures, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23234AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23234AT\"></sup>paralytics, and he healed them.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23235AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23235AU\"></sup>And great crowds followed him from Galilee and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23235AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23235AV\"></sup>Decapolis, and from Jerusalem and Judea, and from beyond the Jordan."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Seeing the crowds, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23236A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23236A\"></sup>he went up on the mountain, and when he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23236B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23236B\"></sup>sat down, his disciples came to him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23237C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23237C\"></sup>he opened his mouth and taught them, saying:",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23238D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23238D\"></sup>“Blessed are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23238E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23238E\"></sup>the poor in spirit, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23238F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23238F\"></sup>theirs is the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Blessed are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23239G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23239G\"></sup>those who mourn, for they shall be comforted.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Blessed are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23240H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23240H\"></sup>meek, for they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23240I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23240I\"></sup>shall inherit the earth.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Blessed are those who hunger and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23241J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23241J\"></sup>thirst <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23241K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23241K\"></sup>for righteousness, for they shall be satisfied.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Blessed are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23242L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23242L\"></sup>the merciful, for they shall receive mercy.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Blessed are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23243M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23243M\"></sup>the pure in heart, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23243N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23243N\"></sup>they shall see God.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Blessed are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23244O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23244O\"></sup>the peacemakers, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23244P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23244P\"></sup>they shall be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23244Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23244Q\"></sup>sons of God.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23245R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23245R\"></sup>“Blessed are those who are persecuted for righteousness' sake, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23245S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23245S\"></sup>theirs is the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23246T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23246T\"></sup>“Blessed are you when others revile you and persecute you and utter all kinds of evil against you falsely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23246U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23246U\"></sup>on my account.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23247V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23247V\"></sup>Rejoice and be glad, for your reward is great in heaven, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23247W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23247W\"></sup>so they persecuted the prophets who were before you.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“You are the salt of the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23248X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23248X\"></sup>but if salt has lost its taste, how shall its saltiness be restored? It is no longer good for anything except to be thrown out and trampled under people's feet.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23249Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23249Y\"></sup>“You are the light of the world. A city set on a hill cannot be hidden.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23250Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23250Z\"></sup>Nor do people light a lamp and put it under a basket, but on a stand, and it gives light to all in the house.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In the same way, let your light shine before others, so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23251AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23251AA\"></sup>that they may see your good works and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23251AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23251AB\"></sup>give glory to your Father who is in heaven.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23252AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23252AC\"></sup>“Do not think that I have come to abolish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23252AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23252AD\"></sup>the Law or the Prophets; I have not come to abolish them but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23252AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23252AE\"></sup>to fulfill them.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23253AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23253AF\"></sup>until heaven and earth pass away, not an iota, not a dot, will pass from the Law until all is accomplished.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23254AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23254AG\"></sup>Therefore whoever relaxes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23254AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23254AH\"></sup>one of the least of these commandments and teaches others to do the same will be called least <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23254AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23254AI\"></sup>in the kingdom of heaven, but whoever does them and teaches them will be called great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23254AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23254AJ\"></sup>in the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For I tell you, unless your righteousness exceeds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23255AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23255AK\"></sup>that of the scribes and Pharisees, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23255AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23255AL\"></sup>will never enter the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23256AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23256AM\"></sup>“You have heard that it was said to those of old, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23256AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23256AN\"></sup>‘You shall not murder; and whoever murders will be liable <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23256AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23256AO\"></sup>to judgment.’</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But I say to you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23257AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23257AP\"></sup>everyone who is angry with his brother will be liable <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23257AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23257AQ\"></sup>to judgment; whoever insults his brother will be liable to the council; and whoever says, ‘You fool!’ will be liable to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23257AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23257AR\"></sup>the hell of fire.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23258AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23258AS\"></sup>So if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23258AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23258AT\"></sup>you are offering your gift at the altar and there remember that your brother has something against you,</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>leave your gift there before the altar and go. First be reconciled to your brother, and then come and offer your gift.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23260AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23260AU\"></sup>Come to terms quickly with your accuser while you are going with him to court, lest your accuser hand you over to the judge, and the judge to the guard, and you be put in prison.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23261AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23261AV\"></sup>you will never get out until you have paid the last penny.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23262AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23262AW\"></sup>“You have heard that it was said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23262AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23262AX\"></sup>‘You shall not commit adultery.’</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But I say to you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23263AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23263AY\"></sup>everyone who looks at a woman with lustful intent has already committed adultery with her in his heart.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23264AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23264AZ\"></sup>If your right eye <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23264BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23264BA\"></sup>causes you to sin, tear it out and throw it away. For it is better that you lose one of your members than that your whole body be thrown into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23264BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23264BB\"></sup>hell.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23265BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23265BC\"></sup>And if your right hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23265BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23265BD\"></sup>causes you to sin, cut it off and throw it away. For it is better that you lose one of your members than that your whole body go into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23265BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23265BE\"></sup>hell.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23266BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23266BF\"></sup>“It was also said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23266BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23266BG\"></sup>‘Whoever divorces his wife, let him give her a certificate of divorce.’</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23267BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23267BH\"></sup>But I say to you that everyone who divorces his wife, except on the ground of sexual immorality, makes her commit adultery, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23267BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23267BI\"></sup>whoever marries a divorced woman commits adultery.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23268BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23268BJ\"></sup>you have heard that it was said to those of old, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23268BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23268BK\"></sup>‘You shall not swear falsely, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23268BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23268BL\"></sup>shall perform to the Lord what you have sworn.’</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23269BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23269BM\"></sup>Do not take an oath at all, either by heaven, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23269BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23269BN\"></sup>it is the throne of God,</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>or by the earth, for it is his footstool, or by Jerusalem, for it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23270BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23270BO\"></sup>the city of the great King.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And do not take an oath by your head, for you cannot make one hair white or black.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Let what you say be simply ‘Yes’ or ‘No’; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23272BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23272BP\"></sup>anything more than this comes from evil.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23273BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23273BQ\"></sup>“You have heard that it was said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23273BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23273BR\"></sup>‘An eye for an eye and a tooth for a tooth.’</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>But I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23274BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23274BS\"></sup>Do not resist the one who is evil. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23274BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23274BT\"></sup>if anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23274BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23274BU\"></sup>slaps you on the right cheek, turn to him the other also.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23275BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23275BV\"></sup>if anyone would sue you and take your tunic, let him have your cloak as well.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And if anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23276BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23276BW\"></sup>forces you to go one mile, go with him two miles.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23277BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23277BX\"></sup>Give to the one who begs from you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23277BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23277BY\"></sup>do not refuse the one who would borrow from you.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23278BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23278BZ\"></sup>“You have heard that it was said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23278CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23278CA\"></sup>‘You shall love your neighbor and hate your enemy.’</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>But I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23279CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23279CB\"></sup>Love your enemies and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23279CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23279CC\"></sup>pray for those who persecute you,</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23280CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23280CD\"></sup>so that you may be sons of your Father who is in heaven. For he makes his sun rise on the evil and on the good, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23280CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23280CE\"></sup>sends rain on the just and on the unjust.</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23281CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23281CF\"></sup>For if you love those who love you, what reward do you have? Do not even the tax collectors do the same?</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>And if you greet only your brothers, what more are you doing than others? Do not even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23282CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23282CG\"></sup>the Gentiles do the same?</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23283CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23283CH\"></sup>You therefore must be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23283CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23283CI\"></sup>perfect, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23283CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23283CJ\"></sup>as your heavenly Father is perfect.</span>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>“Beware of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23284A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23284A\"></sup>practicing your righteousness before other people in order <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23284B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23284B\"></sup>to be seen by them, for then you will have no reward from your Father who is in heaven.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23285C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23285C\"></sup>“Thus, when you give to the needy, sound no trumpet before you, as the hypocrites do in the synagogues and in the streets, that they may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23285D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23285D\"></sup>be praised by others. Truly, I say to you, they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23285E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23285E\"></sup>received their reward.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But when you give to the needy, do not let your left hand know what your right hand is doing,</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>so that your giving may be in secret. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23287F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23287F\"></sup>And your Father who sees in secret will reward you.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“And when you pray, you must not be like the hypocrites. For they love <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23288G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23288G\"></sup>to stand and pray in the synagogues and at the street corners, that they may be seen by others. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23288H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23288H\"></sup>Truly, I say to you, they have received their reward.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But when you pray, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23289I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23289I\"></sup>go into your room and shut the door and pray to your Father who is in secret. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23289J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23289J\"></sup>And your Father who sees in secret will reward you.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“And when you pray, do not heap up empty phrases as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23290K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23290K\"></sup>the Gentiles do, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23290L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23290L\"></sup>they think that they will be heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23290M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23290M\"></sup>for their many words.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Do not be like them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23291N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23291N\"></sup>for your Father knows what you need before you ask him.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23292O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23292O\"></sup>Pray then like this:</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23292P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23292P\"></sup>“Our Father in heaven,</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23292Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23292Q\"></sup>hallowed be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23292R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23292R\"></sup>your name.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23293S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23293S\"></sup>Your kingdom come,</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23293T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23293T\"></sup>your will be done,</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23293U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23293U\"></sup>on earth as it is in heaven.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23294V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23294V\"></sup>Give us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23294W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23294W\"></sup>this day our daily bread,</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and forgive us our debts,</span><span class=\"woj\">as we also have forgiven our debtors.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23296X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23296X\"></sup>lead us not into temptation,</span><span class=\"woj\">but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23296Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23296Y\"></sup>deliver us from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23296Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23296Z\"></sup>evil.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23297AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23297AA\"></sup>For if you forgive others their trespasses, your heavenly Father will also forgive you,</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23298AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23298AB\"></sup>but if you do not forgive others their trespasses, neither will your Father forgive your trespasses.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23299AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23299AC\"></sup>when you fast, do not look gloomy like the hypocrites, for they disfigure their faces that their fasting may be seen by others. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23299AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23299AD\"></sup>Truly, I say to you, they have received their reward.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But when you fast, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23300AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23300AE\"></sup>anoint your head and wash your face,</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>that your fasting may not be seen by others but by your Father who is in secret. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23301AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23301AF\"></sup>And your Father who sees in secret will reward you.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23302AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23302AG\"></sup>“Do not lay up for yourselves treasures on earth, where <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23302AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23302AH\"></sup>moth and rust destroy and where thieves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23302AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23302AI\"></sup>break in and steal,</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23303AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23303AJ\"></sup>but lay up for yourselves treasures in heaven, where neither moth nor rust destroys and where thieves do not break in and steal.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For where your treasure is, there your heart will be also.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23305AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23305AK\"></sup>“The eye is the lamp of the body. So, if your eye is healthy, your whole body will be full of light,</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23306AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23306AL\"></sup>but if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23306AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23306AM\"></sup>your eye is bad, your whole body will be full of darkness. If then the light in you is darkness, how great is the darkness!</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23307AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23307AN\"></sup>“No one can serve two masters, for either he will hate the one and love the other, or he will be devoted to the one and despise the other. You cannot serve God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23307AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23307AO\"></sup>money.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23308AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23308AP\"></sup>“Therefore I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23308AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23308AQ\"></sup>do not be anxious about your life, what you will eat or what you will drink, nor about your body, what you will put on. Is not life more than food, and the body more than clothing?</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23309AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23309AR\"></sup>Look at the birds of the air: they neither sow nor reap nor gather into barns, and yet your heavenly Father feeds them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23309AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23309AS\"></sup>Are you not of more value than they?</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And which of you by being anxious can add a single hour to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23310AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23310AT\"></sup>span of life?</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And why are you anxious about clothing? Consider the lilies of the field, how they grow: they neither toil nor spin,</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>yet I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23312AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23312AU\"></sup>even Solomon in all his glory was not arrayed like one of these.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But if God so clothes the grass of the field, which today is alive and tomorrow is thrown into the oven, will he not much more clothe you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23313AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23313AV\"></sup>O you of little faith?</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Therefore do not be anxious, saying, ‘What shall we eat?’ or ‘What shall we drink?’ or ‘What shall we wear?’</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23315AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23315AW\"></sup>the Gentiles seek after all these things, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23315AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23315AX\"></sup>your heavenly Father knows that you need them all.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23316AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23316AY\"></sup>seek first <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23316AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23316AZ\"></sup>the kingdom of God and his righteousness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23316BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23316BA\"></sup>and all these things will be added to you.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23317BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23317BB\"></sup>“Therefore do not be anxious about tomorrow, for tomorrow will be anxious for itself. Sufficient for the day is its own trouble.</span>"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23318A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23318A\"></sup>“Judge not, that you be not judged.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23319B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23319B\"></sup>For with the judgment you pronounce you will be judged, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23319C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23319C\"></sup>with the measure you use it will be measured to you.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Why do you see the speck that is in your brother's eye, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23320D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23320D\"></sup>do not notice the log that is in your own eye?</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Or how can you say to your brother, ‘Let me take the speck out of your eye,’ when there is the log in your own eye?</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You hypocrite, first take the log out of your own eye, and then you will see clearly to take the speck out of your brother's eye.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23323E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23323E\"></sup>“Do not give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23323F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23323F\"></sup>dogs what is holy, and do not throw your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23323G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23323G\"></sup>pearls before pigs, lest they trample them underfoot and turn to attack you.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23324H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23324H\"></sup>“Ask, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23324I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23324I\"></sup>and it will be given to you; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23324J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23324J\"></sup>seek, and you will find; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23324K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23324K\"></sup>knock, and it will be opened to you.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For everyone who asks receives, and the one who seeks finds, and to the one who knocks it will be opened.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Or which one of you, if his son asks him for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23326L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23326L\"></sup>bread, will give him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23326M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23326M\"></sup>a stone?</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Or if he asks for a fish, will give him a serpent?</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If you then, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23328N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23328N\"></sup>who are evil, know how to give good gifts to your children, how much more will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23328O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23328O\"></sup>your Father who is in heaven give good things to those who ask him!</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23329P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23329P\"></sup>whatever you wish that others would do to you, do also to them, for this is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23329Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23329Q\"></sup>the Law and the Prophets.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23330R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23330R\"></sup>“Enter by the narrow gate. For the gate is wide and the way is easy that leads to destruction, and those who enter by it are many.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For the gate is narrow and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23331S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23331S\"></sup>the way is hard that leads to life, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23331T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23331T\"></sup>those who find it are few.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23332U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23332U\"></sup>“Beware of false prophets, who come to you in sheep's clothing but inwardly are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23332V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23332V\"></sup>ravenous wolves.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You will recognize them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23333W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23333W\"></sup>by their fruits. Are grapes gathered from thornbushes, or figs from thistles?</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23334X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23334X\"></sup>every healthy tree bears good fruit, but the diseased tree bears bad fruit.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>A healthy tree cannot bear bad fruit, nor can a diseased tree bear good fruit.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23336Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23336Y\"></sup>Every tree that does not bear good fruit is cut down and thrown into the fire.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Thus you will recognize them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23337Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23337Z\"></sup>by their fruits.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23338AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23338AA\"></sup>“Not everyone who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23338AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23338AB\"></sup>says to me, ‘Lord, Lord,’ will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23338AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23338AC\"></sup>enter the kingdom of heaven, but the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23338AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23338AD\"></sup>does the will of my Father who is in heaven.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23339AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23339AE\"></sup>On that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23339AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23339AF\"></sup>many will say to me, ‘Lord, Lord, did we not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23339AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23339AG\"></sup>prophesy in your name, and cast out demons <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23339AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23339AH\"></sup>in your name, and do many mighty works in your name?’</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23340AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23340AI\"></sup>And then will I declare to them, ‘I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23340AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23340AJ\"></sup>never knew you; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23340AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23340AK\"></sup>depart from me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23340AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23340AL\"></sup>you workers of lawlessness.’</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23341AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23341AM\"></sup>“Everyone then who hears these words of mine and does them will be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23341AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23341AN\"></sup>a wise man who built his house on the rock.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And the rain fell, and the floods came, and the winds blew and beat on that house, but it did not fall, because it had been founded on the rock.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And everyone who hears these words of mine and does not do them will be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23343AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23343AO\"></sup>a foolish man who built his house on the sand.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And the rain fell, and the floods came, and the winds blew and beat against that house, and it fell, and great was the fall of it.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And when Jesus finished these sayings, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23345AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23345AP\"></sup>the crowds were astonished at his teaching,",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23346AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23346AQ\"></sup>for he was teaching them as one who had authority, and not as their scribes."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>When he came down from the mountain, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23347A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23347A\"></sup>great crowds followed him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23348B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23348B\"></sup>And behold, a leper came to him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23348C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23348C\"></sup>knelt before him, saying, “Lord, if you will, you can make me clean.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And Jesus stretched out his hand and touched him, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“I will; be clean.”</span> And immediately his leprosy was cleansed.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23350D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23350D\"></sup>“See that you say nothing to anyone, but go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23350E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23350E\"></sup>show yourself to the priest and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23350F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23350F\"></sup>offer the gift that Moses commanded, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23350G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23350G\"></sup>for a proof to them.”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23351H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23351H\"></sup>When he had entered Capernaum, a centurion came forward to him, appealing to him,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Lord, my servant is lying paralyzed at home, suffering terribly.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“I will come and heal him.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But the centurion replied, “Lord, I am not worthy to have you come under my roof, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23354I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23354I\"></sup>only say the word, and my servant will be healed.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For I too am a man under authority, with soldiers under me. And I say to one, ‘Go,’ and he goes, and to another, ‘Come,’ and he comes, and to my servant, ‘Do this,’ and he does it.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When Jesus heard this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23356J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23356J\"></sup>he marveled and said to those who followed him, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I tell you, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23356K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23356K\"></sup>no one in Israel have I found such faith.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23357L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23357L\"></sup>many will come from east and west and recline at table with Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob in the kingdom of heaven,</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23358M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23358M\"></sup>while the sons of the kingdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23358N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23358N\"></sup>will be thrown into the outer darkness. In that place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23358O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23358O\"></sup>there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And to the centurion Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Go; let it be done for you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23359P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23359P\"></sup>as you have believed.”</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23359Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23359Q\"></sup>And the servant was healed at that very moment.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23360R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23360R\"></sup>And when Jesus entered Peter's house, he saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23360S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23360S\"></sup>his mother-in-law lying sick with a fever.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23361T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23361T\"></sup>touched her hand, and the fever left her, and she rose and began to serve him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>That evening they brought to him many who were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23362U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23362U\"></sup>oppressed by demons, and he cast out the spirits <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23362V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23362V\"></sup>with a word and healed all who were sick.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23363W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23363W\"></sup>This was to fulfill what was spoken by the prophet Isaiah: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23363X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23363X\"></sup>“He took our illnesses and bore our diseases.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23364Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23364Y\"></sup>when Jesus saw a crowd around him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23364Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23364Z\"></sup>he gave orders to go over to the other side.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23365AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23365AA\"></sup>And a scribe came up and said to him, “Teacher, I will follow you wherever you go.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Foxes have holes, and birds of the air have nests, but the Son of Man has nowhere to lay his head.”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Another of the disciples said to him, “Lord, let me first go and bury my father.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Follow me, and leave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23368AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23368AB\"></sup>the dead to bury their own dead.”</span>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23369AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23369AC\"></sup>And when he got into the boat, his disciples followed him.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And behold, there arose a great storm on the sea, so that the boat was being swamped by the waves; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23370AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23370AD\"></sup>he was asleep.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And they went and woke him, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23371AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23371AE\"></sup>“Save us, Lord; we are perishing.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Why are you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23372AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23372AF\"></sup>afraid, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23372AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23372AG\"></sup>O you of little faith?”</span> Then he rose and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23372AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23372AH\"></sup>rebuked the winds and the sea, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23372AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23372AI\"></sup>there was a great calm.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And the men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23373AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23373AJ\"></sup>marveled, saying, “What sort of man is this, that even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23373AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23373AK\"></sup>winds and sea obey him?”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23374AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23374AL\"></sup>And when he came to the other side, to the country of the Gadarenes, two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23374AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23374AM\"></sup>demon-possessed men met him, coming out of the tombs, so fierce that no one could pass that way.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And behold, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23375AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23375AN\"></sup>cried out, “What have you to do with us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23375AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23375AO\"></sup>O Son of God? Have you come here to torment us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23375AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23375AP\"></sup>before the time?”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Now a herd of many pigs was feeding at some distance from them.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And the demons begged him, saying, “If you cast us out, send us away into the herd of pigs.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Go.”</span> So they came out and went into the pigs, and behold, the whole herd rushed down the steep bank into the sea and drowned in the waters.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>The herdsmen fled, and going into the city they told everything, especially what had happened to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23379AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23379AQ\"></sup>demon-possessed men.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And behold, all the city came out to meet Jesus, and when they saw him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23380AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23380AR\"></sup>they begged him to leave their region."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>And getting into a boat he crossed over and came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23381A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23381A\"></sup>his own city.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23382B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23382B\"></sup>And behold, some people brought to him a paralytic, lying on a bed. And when Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23382C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23382C\"></sup>saw their faith, he said to the paralytic, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23382D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23382D\"></sup>“Take heart, my son; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23382E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23382E\"></sup>your sins are forgiven.”</span>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And behold, some of the scribes said to themselves, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23383F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23383F\"></sup>“This man is blaspheming.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23384G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23384G\"></sup>knowing their thoughts, said, <span class=\"woj\">“Why do you think evil in your hearts?</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For which is easier, to say, ‘Your sins are forgiven,’ or to say, ‘Rise and walk’?</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But that you may know that the Son of Man has authority on earth to forgive sins”</span>—he then said to the paralytic—<span class=\"woj\">“Rise, pick up your bed and go home.”</span>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And he rose and went home.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When the crowds saw it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23388H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23388H\"></sup>they were afraid, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23388I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23388I\"></sup>they glorified God, who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23388J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23388J\"></sup>given such authority to men.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23389K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23389K\"></sup>As Jesus passed on from there, he saw a man called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23389L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23389L\"></sup>Matthew sitting at the tax booth, and he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Follow me.”</span> And he rose and followed him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And as Jesus reclined at table in the house, behold, many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23390M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23390M\"></sup>tax collectors and sinners came and were reclining with Jesus and his disciples.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And when the Pharisees saw this, they said to his disciples, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23391N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23391N\"></sup>“Why does your teacher eat with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23391O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23391O\"></sup>tax collectors and sinners?”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But when he heard it, he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Those who are well have no need of a physician, but those who are sick.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Go and learn <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23393P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23393P\"></sup>what this means: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23393Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23393Q\"></sup>‘I desire mercy, and not sacrifice.’ For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23393R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23393R\"></sup>I came not to call the righteous, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23393S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23393S\"></sup>but sinners.”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23394T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23394T\"></sup>the disciples of John came to him, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23394U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23394U\"></sup>“Why do we and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23394V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23394V\"></sup>the Pharisees fast, but your disciples do not fast?”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23395W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23395W\"></sup>“Can the wedding guests mourn as long as the bridegroom is with them? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23395X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23395X\"></sup>The days will come when the bridegroom is taken away from them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23395Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23395Y\"></sup>then they will fast.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>No one puts a piece of unshrunk cloth on an old garment, for the patch tears away from the garment, and a worse tear is made.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Neither is new wine put into old <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23397Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23397Z\"></sup>wineskins. If it is, the skins burst and the wine is spilled and the skins are destroyed. But new wine is put into fresh wineskins, and so both are preserved.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23398AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23398AA\"></sup>While he was saying these things to them, behold, a ruler came in and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23398AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23398AB\"></sup>knelt before him, saying, “My daughter has just died, but come and lay your hand on her, and she will live.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And Jesus rose and followed him, with his disciples.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And behold, a woman <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23400AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23400AC\"></sup>who had suffered from a discharge of blood for twelve years came up behind him and touched <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23400AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23400AD\"></sup>the fringe of his garment,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>for she said to herself, “If I only touch his garment, I will be made well.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Jesus turned, and seeing her he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23402AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23402AE\"></sup>“Take heart, daughter; your faith has made you well.”</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23402AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23402AF\"></sup>And instantly the woman was made well.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And when Jesus came to the ruler's house and saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23403AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23403AG\"></sup>the flute players and the crowd making a commotion,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Go away, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23404AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23404AH\"></sup>the girl is not dead but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23404AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23404AI\"></sup>sleeping.”</span> And they laughed at him.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23405AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23405AJ\"></sup>when the crowd had been put outside, he went in and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23405AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23405AK\"></sup>took her by the hand, and the girl arose.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And the report of this went through all that district.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23407AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23407AL\"></sup>And as Jesus passed on from there, two blind men followed him, crying aloud, “Have mercy on us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23407AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23407AM\"></sup>Son of David.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When he entered the house, the blind men came to him, and Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you believe that I am able to do this?”</span> They said to him, “Yes, Lord.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23409AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23409AN\"></sup>Then he touched their eyes, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23409AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23409AO\"></sup>“According to your faith be it done to you.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And their eyes were opened. And Jesus sternly warned them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23410AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23410AP\"></sup>“See that no one knows about it.”</span>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23411AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23411AQ\"></sup>But they went away and spread his fame through all that district.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>As they were going away, behold, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23412AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23412AR\"></sup>demon-oppressed man who was mute <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23412AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23412AS\"></sup>was brought to him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And when the demon had been cast out, the mute man spoke. And the crowds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23413AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23413AT\"></sup>marveled, saying, “Never was anything like this seen in Israel.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But the Pharisees said, “He casts out demons by the prince of demons.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23415AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23415AU\"></sup>And Jesus went throughout all the cities and villages, teaching in their synagogues and proclaiming the gospel of the kingdom and healing every disease and every affliction.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23416AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23416AV\"></sup>When he saw the crowds, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23416AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23416AW\"></sup>he had compassion for them, because they were harassed and helpless, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23416AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23416AX\"></sup>like sheep without a shepherd.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23417AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23417AY\"></sup>Then he said to his disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“The harvest is plentiful, but the laborers are few;</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23418AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23418AZ\"></sup>pray earnestly to the Lord of the harvest to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23418BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23418BA\"></sup>send out laborers into his harvest.”</span>"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23419A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23419A\"></sup>And he called to him his twelve disciples and gave them authority over unclean spirits, to cast them out, and to heal every disease and every affliction.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23420B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23420B\"></sup>The names of the twelve apostles are these: first, Simon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23420C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23420C\"></sup>who is called Peter, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23420D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23420D\"></sup>Andrew his brother; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23420E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23420E\"></sup>James the son of Zebedee, and John his brother;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Philip and Bartholomew; Thomas and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23421F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23421F\"></sup>Matthew the tax collector; James the son of Alphaeus, and Thaddaeus;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Simon the Zealot, and Judas Iscariot, who betrayed him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23423G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23423G\"></sup>These twelve Jesus sent out, instructing them, <span class=\"woj\">“Go nowhere among the Gentiles and enter no town of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23423H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23423H\"></sup>the Samaritans,</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23424I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23424I\"></sup>but go rather to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23424J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23424J\"></sup>the lost sheep of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23424K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23424K\"></sup>the house of Israel.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And proclaim as you go, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23425L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23425L\"></sup>‘The kingdom of heaven is at hand.’</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23426M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23426M\"></sup>Heal the sick, raise the dead, cleanse lepers, cast out demons. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23426N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23426N\"></sup>You received without paying; give without pay.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23427O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23427O\"></sup>Acquire no gold or silver or copper for your belts,</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>no bag for your journey, or two tunics or sandals or a staff, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23428P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23428P\"></sup>the laborer deserves his food.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And whatever town or village you enter, find out who is worthy in it and stay there until you depart.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>As you enter the house, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23430Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23430Q\"></sup>greet it.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And if the house is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23431R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23431R\"></sup>worthy, let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23431S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23431S\"></sup>your peace come upon it, but if it is not worthy, let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23431T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23431T\"></sup>your peace return to you.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And if anyone will not receive you or listen to your words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23432U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23432U\"></sup>shake off the dust from your feet when you leave that house or town.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23433V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23433V\"></sup>it will be more bearable on the day of judgment for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23433W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23433W\"></sup>the land of Sodom and Gomorrah than for that town.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23434X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23434X\"></sup>“Behold, I am sending you out as sheep in the midst of wolves, so be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23434Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23434Y\"></sup>wise as serpents and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23434Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23434Z\"></sup>innocent as doves.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Beware of men, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23435AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23435AA\"></sup>they will deliver you over to courts and flog you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23435AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23435AB\"></sup>in their synagogues,</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23436AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23436AC\"></sup>and you will be dragged before governors and kings for my sake, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23436AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23436AD\"></sup>to bear witness before them and the Gentiles.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23437AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23437AE\"></sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23437AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23437AF\"></sup>they deliver you over, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23437AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23437AG\"></sup>do not be anxious how you are to speak or what you are to say, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23437AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23437AH\"></sup>what you are to say will be given to you in that hour.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23438AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23438AI\"></sup>For it is not you who speak, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23438AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23438AJ\"></sup>the Spirit of your Father speaking through you.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23439AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23439AK\"></sup>Brother will deliver brother over to death, and the father his child, and children will rise against parents and have them put to death,</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23440AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23440AL\"></sup>and you will be hated by all for my name's sake. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23440AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23440AM\"></sup>But the one who endures to the end will be saved.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23441AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23441AN\"></sup>persecute you in one town, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23441AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23441AO\"></sup>flee to the next, for truly, I say to you, you will not have gone through all the towns of Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23441AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23441AP\"></sup>before the Son of Man comes.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23442AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23442AQ\"></sup>“A disciple is not above his teacher, nor a servant above his master.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>It is enough for the disciple to be like his teacher, and the servant like his master. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23443AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23443AR\"></sup>If they have called the master of the house Beelzebul, how much more will they malign those of his household.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“So have no fear of them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23444AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23444AS\"></sup>for nothing is covered that will not be revealed, or hidden that will not be known.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>What I tell you in the dark, say in the light, and what you hear whispered, proclaim on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23445AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23445AT\"></sup>the housetops.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23446AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23446AU\"></sup>do not fear those who kill the body but cannot kill the soul. Rather fear him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23446AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23446AV\"></sup>who can destroy both soul and body in hell.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Are not two sparrows sold for a penny? And not one of them will fall to the ground apart from your Father.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23448AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23448AW\"></sup>even the hairs of your head are all numbered.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Fear not, therefore; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23449AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23449AX\"></sup>you are of more value than many sparrows.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23450AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23450AY\"></sup>So everyone who acknowledges me before men, I also will acknowledge before my Father who is in heaven,</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23451AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23451AZ\"></sup>whoever denies me before men, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23451BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23451BA\"></sup>I also will deny before my Father who is in heaven.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23452BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23452BB\"></sup>“Do not think that I have come to bring peace to the earth. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23452BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23452BC\"></sup>I have not come to bring peace, but a sword.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23453BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23453BD\"></sup>For I have come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23453BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23453BE\"></sup>to set a man against his father, and a daughter against her mother, and a daughter-in-law against her mother-in-law.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23454BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23454BF\"></sup>And a person's enemies will be those of his own household.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23455BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23455BG\"></sup>Whoever loves father or mother more than me is not worthy of me, and whoever loves son or daughter more than me is not worthy of me.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23456BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23456BH\"></sup>whoever does not take his cross and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23456BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23456BI\"></sup>follow me is not worthy of me.</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23457BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23457BJ\"></sup>Whoever finds his life will lose it, and whoever loses his life for my sake will find it.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23458BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23458BK\"></sup>“Whoever receives you receives me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23458BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23458BL\"></sup>whoever receives me receives him who sent me.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23459BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23459BM\"></sup>The one who receives a prophet because he is a prophet will receive a prophet's reward, and the one who receives a righteous person because he is a righteous person will receive a righteous person's reward.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23460BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23460BN\"></sup>whoever gives one of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23460BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23460BO\"></sup>these little ones even a cup of cold water because he is a disciple, truly, I say to you, he will by no means lose his reward.”</span>"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>When Jesus had finished instructing his twelve disciples, he went on from there to teach and preach in their cities.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23462A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23462A\"></sup>Now when John heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23462B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23462B\"></sup>in prison about the deeds of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23462C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23462C\"></sup>the Christ, he sent word by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23462D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23462D\"></sup>his disciples",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and said to him, “Are you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23463E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23463E\"></sup>the one who is to come, or shall we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23463F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23463F\"></sup>look for another?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Go and tell John what you hear and see:</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23465G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23465G\"></sup>the blind receive their sight and the lame walk, lepers are cleansed and the deaf hear, and the dead are raised up, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23465H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23465H\"></sup>the poor have good news preached to them.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And blessed is the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23466I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23466I\"></sup>is not offended by me.”</span>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>As they went away, Jesus began to speak to the crowds concerning John: <span class=\"woj\">“What did you go out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23467J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23467J\"></sup>into the wilderness to see? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23467K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23467K\"></sup>A reed shaken by the wind?</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>What then did you go out to see? A man dressed in soft clothing? Behold, those who wear soft clothing are in kings' houses.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>What then did you go out to see? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23469L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23469L\"></sup>A prophet? Yes, I tell you, and more than a prophet.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This is he of whom it is written,</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23470M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23470M\"></sup>“‘Behold, I send my messenger before your face,</span><span class=\"woj\">who will prepare your way before you.’</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Truly, I say to you, among those born of women there has arisen no one greater than John the Baptist. Yet the one who is least in the kingdom of heaven is greater than he.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23472N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23472N\"></sup>From the days of John the Baptist until now the kingdom of heaven has suffered violence, and the violent take it by force.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23473O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23473O\"></sup>For all the Prophets and the Law prophesied until John,</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and if you are willing to accept it, he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23474P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23474P\"></sup>Elijah who is to come.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23475Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23475Q\"></sup>He who has ears to hear, let him hear.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“But to what shall I compare this generation? It is like children sitting in the marketplaces and calling to their playmates,</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“‘We played the flute for you, and you did not dance;</span><span class=\"woj\">we sang a dirge, and you did not mourn.’</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For John came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23478R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23478R\"></sup>neither eating <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23478S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23478S\"></sup>nor drinking, and they say, ‘He has a demon.’</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The Son of Man came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23479T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23479T\"></sup>eating and drinking, and they say, ‘Look at him! A glutton and a drunkard, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23479U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23479U\"></sup>a friend of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23479V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23479V\"></sup>tax collectors and sinners!’ Yet wisdom is justified by her deeds.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23480W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23480W\"></sup>Then he began to denounce the cities where most of his mighty works had been done, because they did not repent.",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23481X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23481X\"></sup>“Woe to you, Chorazin! Woe to you, Bethsaida! For if the mighty works done in you had been done in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23481Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23481Y\"></sup>Tyre and Sidon, they would have repented long ago in sackcloth and ashes.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23482Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23482Z\"></sup>But I tell you, it will be more bearable on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23482AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23482AA\"></sup>the day of judgment for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23482AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23482AB\"></sup>Tyre and Sidon than for you.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23483AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23483AC\"></sup>Capernaum, will you be exalted to heaven? You will be brought down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23483AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23483AD\"></sup>Hades. For if the mighty works done in you had been done in Sodom, it would have remained until this day.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23484AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23484AE\"></sup>But I tell you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23484AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23484AF\"></sup>it will be more tolerable on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23484AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23484AG\"></sup>the day of judgment for the land of Sodom than for you.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23485AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23485AH\"></sup>At that time Jesus declared, <span class=\"woj\">“I thank you, Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23485AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23485AI\"></sup>Lord of heaven and earth, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23485AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23485AJ\"></sup>you have hidden these things from the wise and understanding and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23485AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23485AK\"></sup>revealed them to little children;</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>yes, Father, for such was your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23486AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23486AL\"></sup>gracious will.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23487AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23487AM\"></sup>All things have been handed over to me by my Father, and no one knows the Son <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23487AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23487AN\"></sup>except the Father, and no one knows the Father except the Son and anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23487AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23487AO\"></sup>to whom the Son chooses to reveal him.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23488AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23488AP\"></sup>Come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23488AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23488AQ\"></sup>me, all who labor and are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23488AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23488AR\"></sup>heavy laden, and I will give you rest.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Take my yoke upon you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23489AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23489AS\"></sup>learn from me, for I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23489AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23489AT\"></sup>gentle and lowly in heart, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23489AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23489AU\"></sup>you will find rest for your souls.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23490AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23490AV\"></sup>my yoke is easy, and my burden is light.”</span>"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>At that time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23491A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23491A\"></sup>Jesus went through the grainfields on the Sabbath. His disciples were hungry, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23491B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23491B\"></sup>they began to pluck heads of grain and to eat.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But when the Pharisees saw it, they said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23492C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23492C\"></sup>“Look, your disciples are doing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23492D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23492D\"></sup>what is not lawful to do on the Sabbath.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23493E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23493E\"></sup>“Have you not read what David did when he was hungry, and those who were with him:</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>how he entered the house of God and ate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23494F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23494F\"></sup>the bread of the Presence, which it was not lawful for him to eat nor for those who were with him, but only for the priests?</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Or have you not read <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23495G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23495G\"></sup>in the Law how on the Sabbath the priests in the temple profane the Sabbath and are guiltless?</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23496H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23496H\"></sup>something greater than the temple is here.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And if you had known <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23497I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23497I\"></sup>what this means, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23497J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23497J\"></sup>‘I desire mercy, and not sacrifice,’ you would not have condemned the guiltless.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23498K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23498K\"></sup>the Son of Man is lord of the Sabbath.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He went on from there and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23499L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23499L\"></sup>entered their synagogue.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And a man was there with a withered hand. And they asked him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23500M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23500M\"></sup>“Is it lawful to heal on the Sabbath?”—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23500N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23500N\"></sup>so that they might accuse him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Which one of you who has a sheep, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23501O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23501O\"></sup>if it falls into a pit on the Sabbath, will not take hold of it and lift it out?</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23502P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23502P\"></sup>Of how much more value is a man than a sheep! So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23502Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23502Q\"></sup>it is lawful to do good on the Sabbath.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then he said to the man, <span class=\"woj\">“Stretch out your hand.”</span> And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23503R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23503R\"></sup>the man stretched it out, and it was restored, healthy like the other.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But the Pharisees went out and conspired against him, how to destroy him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Jesus, aware of this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23505S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23505S\"></sup>withdrew from there. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23505T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23505T\"></sup>many followed him, and he healed them all",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23506U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23506U\"></sup>ordered them not to make him known.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23507V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23507V\"></sup>This was to fulfill what was spoken by the prophet Isaiah:",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23508W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23508W\"></sup>“Behold, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23508X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23508X\"></sup>servant whom I have chosen,my beloved with whom my soul is well pleased.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23508Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23508Y\"></sup>I will put my Spirit upon him,and he will proclaim justice to the Gentiles.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He will not quarrel or cry aloud,nor will anyone hear his voice in the streets;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>a bruised reed he will not break,and a smoldering wick he will not quench,until he brings justice to victory;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23511Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23511Z\"></sup>and in his name the Gentiles will hope.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23512AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23512AA\"></sup>Then a demon-oppressed man who was blind and mute was brought to him, and he healed him, so that the man spoke and saw.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23513AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23513AB\"></sup>And all the people were amazed, and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23513AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23513AC\"></sup>“Can this be the Son of David?”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But when the Pharisees heard it, they said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23514AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23514AD\"></sup>“It is only by Beelzebul, the prince of demons, that this man casts out demons.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23515AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23515AE\"></sup>Knowing their thoughts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23515AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23515AF\"></sup>he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Every kingdom divided against itself is laid waste, and no city or house divided against itself will stand.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And if Satan casts out Satan, he is divided against himself. How then will his kingdom stand?</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And if I cast out demons by Beelzebul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23517AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23517AG\"></sup>by whom do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23517AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23517AH\"></sup>your sons cast them out? Therefore they will be your judges.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But if it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23518AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23518AI\"></sup>by the Spirit of God that I cast out demons, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23518AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23518AJ\"></sup>the kingdom of God has come upon you.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23519AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23519AK\"></sup>how can someone enter a strong man's house and plunder his goods, unless he first binds the strong man? Then indeed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23519AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23519AL\"></sup>he may plunder his house.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23520AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23520AM\"></sup>Whoever is not with me is against me, and whoever does not gather with me scatters.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23521AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23521AN\"></sup>Therefore I tell you, every sin and blasphemy will be forgiven people, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23521AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23521AO\"></sup>the blasphemy against the Spirit will not be forgiven.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And whoever speaks a word <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23522AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23522AP\"></sup>against the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23522AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23522AQ\"></sup>will be forgiven, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23522AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23522AR\"></sup>whoever speaks against the Holy Spirit will not be forgiven, either in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23522AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23522AS\"></sup>this age or in the age to come.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23523AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23523AT\"></sup>“Either make the tree good and its fruit good, or make the tree bad and its fruit bad, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23523AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23523AU\"></sup>for the tree is known by its fruit.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23524AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23524AV\"></sup>You brood of vipers! How can you speak good, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23524AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23524AW\"></sup>when you are evil? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23524AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23524AX\"></sup>For out of the abundance of the heart the mouth speaks.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23525AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23525AY\"></sup>The good person out of his good treasure brings forth good, and the evil person out of his evil treasure brings forth evil.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23526AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23526AZ\"></sup>on the day of judgment <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23526BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23526BA\"></sup>people will give account for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23526BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23526BB\"></sup>every careless word they speak,</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23527BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23527BC\"></sup>by your words you will be justified, and by your words you will be condemned.”</span>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Then some of the scribes and Pharisees answered him, saying, “Teacher, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23528BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23528BD\"></sup>we wish to see a sign from you.”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>But he answered them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23529BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23529BE\"></sup>“An evil and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23529BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23529BF\"></sup>adulterous generation seeks for a sign, but no sign will be given to it except the sign of the prophet Jonah.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23530BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23530BG\"></sup>just as Jonah was three days and three nights in the belly of the great fish, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23530BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23530BH\"></sup>so will the Son of Man be three days and three nights in the heart of the earth.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23531BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23531BI\"></sup>The men of Nineveh will rise up at the judgment with this generation and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23531BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23531BJ\"></sup>condemn it, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23531BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23531BK\"></sup>they repented at the preaching of Jonah, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23531BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23531BL\"></sup>something greater than Jonah is here.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23532BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23532BM\"></sup>The queen of the South will rise up at the judgment with this generation and condemn it, for she came from the ends of the earth to hear the wisdom of Solomon, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23532BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23532BN\"></sup>something greater than Solomon is here.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>“When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23533BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23533BO\"></sup>the unclean spirit has gone out of a person, it passes through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23533BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23533BP\"></sup>waterless places seeking rest, but finds none.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Then it says, ‘I will return to my house from which I came.’ And when it comes, it finds the house empty, swept, and put in order.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Then it goes and brings with it seven other spirits more evil than itself, and they enter and dwell there, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23535BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23535BQ\"></sup>the last state of that person is worse than the first. So also will it be with this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23535BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23535BR\"></sup>evil generation.”</span>",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>While he was still speaking to the people, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23536BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23536BS\"></sup>his mother and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23536BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23536BT\"></sup>brothers stood outside, asking to speak to him.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>But he replied to the man who told him, <span class=\"woj\">“Who is my mother, and who are my brothers?”</span>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>And stretching out his hand toward his disciples, he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Here are my mother and my brothers!</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23539BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23539BU\"></sup>whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23539BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23539BV\"></sup>does the will of my Father in heaven is my brother and sister and mother.”</span>"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>That same day Jesus went out of the house <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23540A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23540A\"></sup>and sat beside the sea.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And great crowds gathered about him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23541B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23541B\"></sup>so that he got into a boat and sat down. And the whole crowd stood on the beach.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23542C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23542C\"></sup>he told them many things in parables, saying: <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23542D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23542D\"></sup>“A sower went out to sow.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And as he sowed, some seeds fell along the path, and the birds came and devoured them.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Other seeds fell on rocky ground, where they did not have much soil, and immediately they sprang up, since they had no depth of soil,</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23545E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23545E\"></sup>when the sun rose they were scorched. And since they had no root, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23545F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23545F\"></sup>they withered away.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Other seeds fell among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23546G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23546G\"></sup>thorns, and the thorns grew up and choked them.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Other seeds fell on good soil and produced grain, some <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23547H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23547H\"></sup>a hundredfold, some sixty, some thirty.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23548I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23548I\"></sup>He who has ears, let him hear.”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then the disciples came and said to him, “Why do you speak to them in parables?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And he answered them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23550J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23550J\"></sup>“To you it has been given to know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23550K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23550K\"></sup>the secrets of the kingdom of heaven, but to them it has not been given.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23551L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23551L\"></sup>For to the one who has, more will be given, and he will have an abundance, but from the one who has not, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23551M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23551M\"></sup>even what he has will be taken away.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>This is why I speak to them in parables, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23552N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23552N\"></sup>seeing they do not see, and hearing they do not hear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23552O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23552O\"></sup>nor do they understand.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Indeed, in their case the prophecy of Isaiah is fulfilled that says:</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23553P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23553P\"></sup>“‘“You will indeed hear but never understand,</span><span class=\"woj\">and you will indeed see but never perceive.”</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For this people's heart has grown dull,</span><span class=\"woj\">and with their ears <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23554Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23554Q\"></sup>they can barely hear,</span><span class=\"woj\">and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23554R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23554R\"></sup>their eyes they have closed,</span><span class=\"woj\">lest they should see with their eyes</span><span class=\"woj\">and hear with their ears</span><span class=\"woj\">and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23554S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23554S\"></sup>understand with their heart</span><span class=\"woj\">and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23554T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23554T\"></sup>turn, and I would heal them.’</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23555U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23555U\"></sup>blessed are your eyes, for they see, and your ears, for they hear.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23556V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23556V\"></sup>For truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23556W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23556W\"></sup>many prophets and righteous people longed to see what you see, and did not see it, and to hear what you hear, and did not hear it.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23557X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23557X\"></sup>“Hear then the parable of the sower:</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When anyone hears the word of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23558Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23558Y\"></sup>the kingdom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23558Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23558Z\"></sup>does not understand it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23558AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23558AA\"></sup>the evil one comes and snatches away what has been sown in his heart. This is what was sown along the path.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>As for what was sown on rocky ground, this is the one who hears the word and immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23559AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23559AB\"></sup>receives it with joy,</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>yet he has no root in himself, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23560AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23560AC\"></sup>endures for a while, and when tribulation or persecution arises on account of the word, immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23560AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23560AD\"></sup>he falls away.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>As for what was sown among thorns, this is the one who hears the word, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23561AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23561AE\"></sup>the cares of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23561AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23561AF\"></sup>the world and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23561AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23561AG\"></sup>the deceitfulness of riches choke the word, and it proves unfruitful.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>As for what was sown on good soil, this is the one who hears the word and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23562AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23562AH\"></sup>understands it. He indeed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23562AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23562AI\"></sup>bears fruit and yields, in one case <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23562AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23562AJ\"></sup>a hundredfold, in another sixty, and in another thirty.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He put another parable before them, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23563AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23563AK\"></sup>“The kingdom of heaven may be compared to a man who sowed good seed in his field,</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>but while his men were sleeping, his enemy came and sowed weeds among the wheat and went away.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>So when the plants came up and bore grain, then the weeds appeared also.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And the servants of the master of the house came and said to him, ‘Master, did you not sow good seed in your field? How then does it have weeds?’</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>He said to them, ‘An enemy has done this.’ So the servants said to him, ‘Then do you want us to go and gather them?’</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23568AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23568AL\"></sup>‘No, lest in gathering the weeds you root up the wheat along with them.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Let both grow together until the harvest, and at harvest time I will tell the reapers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23569AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23569AM\"></sup>“Gather the weeds first and bind them in bundles to be burned, but gather the wheat into my barn.”’”</span>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>He put another parable before them, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23570AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23570AN\"></sup>“The kingdom of heaven is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23570AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23570AO\"></sup>a grain of mustard seed that a man took and sowed in his field.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>It is the smallest of all seeds, but when it has grown it is larger than all the garden plants and becomes a tree, so that the birds of the air come and make nests in its branches.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>He told them another parable. <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23572AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23572AP\"></sup>“The kingdom of heaven is like leaven that a woman took and hid in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23572AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23572AQ\"></sup>three measures of flour, till it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23572AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23572AR\"></sup>all leavened.”</span>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23573AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23573AS\"></sup>All these things Jesus said to the crowds in parables; indeed, he said nothing to them without a parable.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>This was to fulfill what was spoken by the prophet:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23574AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23574AT\"></sup>“I will open my mouth in parables;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23574AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23574AU\"></sup>I will utter what has been hidden <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23574AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23574AV\"></sup>since the foundation of the world.”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Then he left the crowds and went into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23575AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23575AW\"></sup>the house. And his disciples came to him, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23575AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23575AX\"></sup>“Explain to us the parable of the weeds of the field.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>He answered, <span class=\"woj\">“The one who sows the good seed is the Son of Man.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>The field is the world, and the good seed is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23577AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23577AY\"></sup>the sons of the kingdom. The weeds are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23577AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23577AZ\"></sup>the sons of the evil one,</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>and the enemy who sowed them is the devil. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23578BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23578BA\"></sup>The harvest is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23578BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23578BB\"></sup>the end of the age, and the reapers are angels.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Just as the weeds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23579BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23579BC\"></sup>are gathered and burned with fire, so will it be at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23579BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23579BD\"></sup>the end of the age.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23580BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23580BE\"></sup>The Son of Man will send his angels, and they will gather out of his kingdom all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23580BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23580BF\"></sup>causes of sin and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23580BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23580BG\"></sup>all law-breakers,</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23581BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23581BH\"></sup>and throw them into the fiery furnace. In that place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23581BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23581BI\"></sup>there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23582BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23582BJ\"></sup>the righteous will shine like the sun <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23582BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23582BK\"></sup>in the kingdom of their Father. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23582BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23582BL\"></sup>He who has ears, let him hear.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>“The kingdom of heaven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23583BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23583BM\"></sup>is like treasure hidden in a field, which a man found and covered up. Then in his joy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23583BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23583BN\"></sup>he goes and sells all that he has and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23583BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23583BO\"></sup>buys that field.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>“Again, the kingdom of heaven is like a merchant in search of fine pearls,</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>who, on finding <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23585BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23585BP\"></sup>one pearl of great value, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23585BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23585BQ\"></sup>went and sold all that he had and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23585BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23585BR\"></sup>bought it.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>“Again, the kingdom of heaven is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23586BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23586BS\"></sup>like a net that was thrown into the sea and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23586BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23586BT\"></sup>gathered fish of every kind.</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>When it was full, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23587BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23587BU\"></sup>men drew it ashore and sat down and sorted the good into containers but threw away the bad.</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>So it will be at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23588BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23588BV\"></sup>the end of the age. The angels will come out and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23588BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23588BW\"></sup>separate the evil from the righteous</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23589BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23589BX\"></sup>and throw them into the fiery furnace. In that place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23589BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23589BY\"></sup>there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth.</span>",
			"51": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23590BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23590BZ\"></sup>“Have you understood all these things?”</span> They said to him, “Yes.”",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Therefore every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23591CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23591CA\"></sup>scribe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23591CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23591CB\"></sup>who has been trained for the kingdom of heaven is like a master of a house, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23591CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23591CC\"></sup>brings out of his treasure what is new and what is old.”</span>",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>And when Jesus had finished these parables, he went away from there,",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23593CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23593CD\"></sup>and coming to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23593CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23593CE\"></sup>his hometown <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23593CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23593CF\"></sup>he taught them in their synagogue, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23593CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23593CG\"></sup>they were astonished, and said, “Where did this man get this wisdom and these mighty works?",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23594CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23594CH\"></sup>Is not this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23594CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23594CI\"></sup>the carpenter's son? Is not his mother called Mary? And are not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23594CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23594CJ\"></sup>his brothers James and Joseph and Simon and Judas?",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>And are not all his sisters with us? Where then did this man get all these things?”",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23596CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23596CK\"></sup>they took offense at him. But Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23596CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23596CL\"></sup>“A prophet is not without honor except in his hometown and in his own household.”</span>",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>And he did not do many mighty works there, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23597CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23597CM\"></sup>because of their unbelief."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23598A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23598A\"></sup>At that time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23598B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23598B\"></sup>Herod the tetrarch heard about the fame of Jesus,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and he said to his servants, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23599C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23599C\"></sup>“This is John the Baptist. He has been raised from the dead; that is why these miraculous powers are at work in him.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23600D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23600D\"></sup>Herod had seized John and bound him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23600E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23600E\"></sup>put him in prison for the sake of Herodias, his brother Philip's wife,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>because John had been saying to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23601F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23601F\"></sup>“It is not lawful for you to have her.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And though he wanted to put him to death, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23602G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23602G\"></sup>he feared the people, because they held him to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23602H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23602H\"></sup>a prophet.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But when Herod's <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23603I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23603I\"></sup>birthday came, the daughter of Herodias danced before the company and pleased Herod,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>so that he promised with an oath to give her whatever she might ask.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Prompted by her mother, she said, “Give me the head of John the Baptist here on a platter.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And the king was sorry, but because of his oaths and his guests he commanded it to be given.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He sent and had John beheaded in the prison,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and his head was brought on a platter and given to the girl, and she brought it to her mother.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23609J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23609J\"></sup>his disciples came and took the body and buried it, and they went and told Jesus.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now when Jesus heard this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23610K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23610K\"></sup>he withdrew from there in a boat to a desolate place by himself. But when the crowds heard it, they followed him on foot from the towns.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>When he went ashore he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23611L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23611L\"></sup>saw a great crowd, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23611M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23611M\"></sup>he had compassion on them and healed their sick.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Now when it was evening, the disciples came to him and said, “This is a desolate place, and the day is now over; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23612N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23612N\"></sup>send the crowds away to go into the villages and buy food for themselves.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“They need not go away; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23613O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23613O\"></sup>you give them something to eat.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They said to him, “We have only five loaves here and two fish.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Bring them here to me.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then he ordered the crowds to sit down on the grass, and taking the five loaves and the two fish, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23616P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23616P\"></sup>he looked up to heaven and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23616Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23616Q\"></sup>said a blessing. Then he broke the loaves and gave them to the disciples, and the disciples gave them to the crowds.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And they all ate and were satisfied. And they took up twelve baskets full of the broken pieces left over.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And those who ate were about five thousand men, besides women and children.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23619R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23619R\"></sup>Immediately he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23619S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23619S\"></sup>made the disciples get into the boat and go before him to the other side, while he dismissed the crowds.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And after he had dismissed the crowds, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23620T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23620T\"></sup>he went up on the mountain by himself to pray. When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23620U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23620U\"></sup>evening came, he was there alone,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>but the boat by this time was a long way from the land, beaten by the waves, for the wind was against them.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23622V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23622V\"></sup>in the fourth watch of the night he came to them, walking on the sea.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But when the disciples saw him walking on the sea, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23623W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23623W\"></sup>they were terrified, and said, “It is a ghost!” and they cried out in fear.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But immediately Jesus spoke to them, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23624X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23624X\"></sup>“Take heart; it is I. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23624Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23624Y\"></sup>Do not be afraid.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And Peter answered him, “Lord, if it is you, command me to come to you on the water.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>He said, <span class=\"woj\">“Come.”</span> So Peter got out of the boat and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23626Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23626Z\"></sup>walked on the water and came to Jesus.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But when he saw the wind, he was afraid, and beginning to sink he cried out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23627AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23627AA\"></sup>“Lord, save me.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Jesus immediately reached out his hand and took hold of him, saying to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23628AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23628AB\"></sup>“O you of little faith, why did you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23628AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23628AC\"></sup>doubt?”</span>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And when they got into the boat, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23629AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23629AD\"></sup>the wind ceased.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23630AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23630AE\"></sup>those in the boat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23630AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23630AF\"></sup>worshiped him, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23630AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23630AG\"></sup>“Truly you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23630AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23630AH\"></sup>the Son of God.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23631AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23631AI\"></sup>And when they had crossed over, they came to land at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23631AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23631AJ\"></sup>Gennesaret.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And when the men of that place recognized him, they sent around to all that region and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23632AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23632AK\"></sup>brought to him all who were sick",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>and implored him that they might only touch <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23633AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23633AL\"></sup>the fringe of his garment. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23633AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23633AM\"></sup>as many as touched it were made well."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23634A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23634A\"></sup>Then Pharisees and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23634B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23634B\"></sup>scribes came to Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23634C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23634C\"></sup>from Jerusalem and said,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23635D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23635D\"></sup>“Why do your disciples break <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23635E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23635E\"></sup>the tradition of the elders? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23635F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23635F\"></sup>For they do not wash their hands when they eat.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“And why do you break the commandment of God for the sake of your tradition?</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For God commanded, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23637G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23637G\"></sup>‘Honor your father and your mother,’ and, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23637H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23637H\"></sup>‘Whoever reviles father or mother must surely die.’</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But you say, ‘If anyone tells his father or his mother, “What you would have gained from me is given to God,”</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>he need not honor his father.’</span> <span class=\"woj\">So for the sake of your tradition you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23639I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23639I\"></sup>made void the word of God.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23640J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23640J\"></sup>You hypocrites! Well did Isaiah prophesy of you, when he said:</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23641K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23641K\"></sup>“‘This people honors me with their lips,</span><span class=\"woj\">but their heart is far from me;</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>in vain do they worship me,</span><span class=\"woj\">teaching as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23642L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23642L\"></sup>doctrines the commandments of men.’”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And he called the people to him and said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23643M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23643M\"></sup>“Hear and understand:</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23644N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23644N\"></sup>it is not what goes into the mouth that defiles a person, but what comes out of the mouth; this defiles a person.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the disciples came and said to him, “Do you know that the Pharisees were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23645O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23645O\"></sup>offended when they heard this saying?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He answered, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23646P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23646P\"></sup>“Every plant that my heavenly Father has not planted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23646Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23646Q\"></sup>will be rooted up.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Let them alone; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23647R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23647R\"></sup>they are blind guides. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23647S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23647S\"></sup>if the blind lead the blind, both will fall into a pit.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But Peter said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23648T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23648T\"></sup>“Explain the parable to us.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23649U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23649U\"></sup>“Are you also still without understanding?</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do you not see that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23650V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23650V\"></sup>whatever goes into the mouth passes into the stomach and is expelled?</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23651W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23651W\"></sup>what comes out of the mouth proceeds from the heart, and this defiles a person.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For out of the heart come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23652X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23652X\"></sup>evil thoughts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23652Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23652Y\"></sup>murder, adultery, sexual immorality, theft, false witness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23652Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23652Z\"></sup>slander.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23653AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23653AA\"></sup>These are what defile a person. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23653AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23653AB\"></sup>to eat with unwashed hands does not defile anyone.”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23654AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23654AC\"></sup>And Jesus went away from there and withdrew to the district of Tyre and Sidon.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23655AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23655AD\"></sup>a Canaanite woman from that region came out and was crying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23655AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23655AE\"></sup>“Have mercy on me, O Lord, Son of David; my daughter is severely oppressed by a demon.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But he did not answer her a word. And his disciples came and begged him, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23656AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23656AF\"></sup>“Send her away, for she is crying out after us.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He answered, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23657AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23657AG\"></sup>“I was sent only to the lost sheep of the house of Israel.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But she came and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23658AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23658AH\"></sup>knelt before him, saying, “Lord, help me.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And he answered, <span class=\"woj\">“It is not right to take the children's bread and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23659AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23659AI\"></sup>throw it to the dogs.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>She said, “Yes, Lord, yet even the dogs eat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23660AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23660AJ\"></sup>the crumbs that fall from their masters' table.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Then Jesus answered her, <span class=\"woj\">“O woman, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23661AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23661AK\"></sup>great is your faith! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23661AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23661AL\"></sup>Be it done for you as you desire.”</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23661AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23661AM\"></sup>And her daughter was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23661AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23661AN\"></sup>healed instantly.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23662AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23662AO\"></sup>Jesus went on from there and walked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23662AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23662AP\"></sup>beside the Sea of Galilee. And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23662AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23662AQ\"></sup>went up on the mountain and sat down there.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And great crowds came to him, bringing with them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23663AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23663AR\"></sup>the lame, the blind, the crippled, the mute, and many others, and they put them at his feet, and he healed them,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23664AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23664AS\"></sup>so that the crowd wondered, when they saw the mute speaking, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23664AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23664AT\"></sup>the crippled healthy, the lame walking, and the blind seeing. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23664AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23664AU\"></sup>they glorified <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23664AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23664AV\"></sup>the God of Israel.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23665AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23665AW\"></sup>Then Jesus called his disciples to him and said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23665AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23665AX\"></sup>“I have compassion on the crowd because they have been with me now three days and have nothing to eat. And I am unwilling to send them away hungry, lest they faint on the way.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And the disciples said to him, “Where are we to get enough bread in such a desolate place to feed so great a crowd?”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“How many loaves do you have?”</span> They said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23667AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23667AY\"></sup>“Seven, and a few small fish.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And directing the crowd to sit down on the ground,",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>he took the seven loaves and the fish, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23669AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23669AZ\"></sup>having given thanks he broke them and gave them to the disciples, and the disciples gave them to the crowds.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23670BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23670BA\"></sup>they all ate and were satisfied. And they took up seven baskets full of the broken pieces left over.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Those who ate were four thousand men, besides women and children.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And after sending away the crowds, he got into the boat and went to the region of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23672BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23672BB\"></sup>Magadan."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23673A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23673A\"></sup>And the Pharisees and Sadducees came, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23673B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23673B\"></sup>to test him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23673C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23673C\"></sup>they asked him to show them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23673D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23673D\"></sup>a sign from heaven.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He answered them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23674E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23674E\"></sup>“When it is evening, you say, ‘It will be fair weather, for the sky is red.’</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And in the morning, ‘It will be stormy today, for the sky is red and threatening.’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23675F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23675F\"></sup>You know how to interpret the appearance of the sky, but you cannot interpret <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23675G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23675G\"></sup>the signs of the times.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23676H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23676H\"></sup>An evil and adulterous generation seeks for a sign, but no sign will be given to it except the sign of Jonah.”</span> So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23676I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23676I\"></sup>he left them and departed.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When the disciples reached the other side, they had forgotten to bring any bread.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Watch and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23678J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23678J\"></sup>beware of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23678K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23678K\"></sup>the leaven of the Pharisees and Sadducees.”</span>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And they began discussing it among themselves, saying, “We brought no bread.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23680L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23680L\"></sup>Jesus, aware of this, said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23680M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23680M\"></sup>“O you of little faith, why are you discussing among yourselves the fact that you have no bread?</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23681N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23681N\"></sup>Do you not yet perceive? Do you not remember <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23681O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23681O\"></sup>the five loaves for the five thousand, and how many baskets you gathered?</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23682P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23682P\"></sup>the seven loaves for the four thousand, and how many baskets you gathered?</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>How is it that you fail to understand that I did not speak about bread? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23683Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23683Q\"></sup>Beware of the leaven of the Pharisees and Sadducees.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23684R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23684R\"></sup>Then they understood that he did not tell them to beware of the leaven of bread, but of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23684S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23684S\"></sup>the teaching of the Pharisees and Sadducees.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23685T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23685T\"></sup>Now when Jesus came into the district of Caesarea Philippi, he asked his disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“Who do people say that the Son of Man is?”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And they said, “Some say <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23686U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23686U\"></sup>John the Baptist, others say <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23686V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23686V\"></sup>Elijah, and others Jeremiah or one of the prophets.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“But who do you say that I am?”</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Simon Peter replied, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23688W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23688W\"></sup>“You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23688X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23688X\"></sup>the Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23688Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23688Y\"></sup>the Son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23688Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23688Z\"></sup>the living God.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23689AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23689AA\"></sup>“Blessed are you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23689AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23689AB\"></sup>Simon Bar-Jonah! For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23689AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23689AC\"></sup>flesh and blood has not revealed this to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23689AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23689AD\"></sup>but my Father who is in heaven.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23690AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23690AE\"></sup>you are Peter, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23690AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23690AF\"></sup>on this rock I will build my church, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23690AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23690AG\"></sup>the gates of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23690AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23690AH\"></sup>hell shall not prevail against it.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I will give you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23691AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23691AI\"></sup>the keys of the kingdom of heaven, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23691AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23691AJ\"></sup>whatever you bind on earth shall be bound in heaven, and whatever you loose on earth shall be loosed in heaven.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23692AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23692AK\"></sup>Then he strictly charged the disciples to tell no one that he was the Christ.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23693AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23693AL\"></sup>From that time Jesus began to show his disciples that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23693AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23693AM\"></sup>he must go to Jerusalem and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23693AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23693AN\"></sup>suffer many things from the elders and chief priests and scribes, and be killed, and on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23693AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23693AO\"></sup>the third day be raised.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And Peter took him aside and began to rebuke him, saying, “Far be it from you, Lord! This shall never happen to you.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But he turned and said to Peter, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23695AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23695AP\"></sup>“Get behind me, Satan! You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23695AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23695AQ\"></sup>a hindrance to me. For you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23695AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23695AR\"></sup>are not setting your mind on the things of God, but on the things of man.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then Jesus told his disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“If anyone would come after me, let him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23696AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23696AS\"></sup>deny himself and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23696AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23696AT\"></sup>take up his cross and follow me.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23697AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23697AU\"></sup>whoever would save his life will lose it, but whoever loses his life for my sake will find it.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23698AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23698AV\"></sup>what will it profit a man if he gains the whole world and forfeits his soul? Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23698AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23698AW\"></sup>what shall a man give in return for his soul?</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23699AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23699AX\"></sup>For the Son of Man is going to come with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23699AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23699AY\"></sup>his angels in the glory of his Father, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23699AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23699AZ\"></sup>then he will repay each person according to what he has done.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Truly, I say to you, there are some standing here who will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23700BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23700BA\"></sup>taste death <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23700BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23700BB\"></sup>until they see the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23700BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23700BC\"></sup>coming in his kingdom.”</span>"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23701A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23701A\"></sup>And after six days Jesus took with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23701B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23701B\"></sup>Peter and James, and John his brother, and led them up a high mountain by themselves.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23702C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23702C\"></sup>transfigured before them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23702D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23702D\"></sup>his face shone like the sun, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23702E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23702E\"></sup>his clothes became white as light.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And behold, there appeared to them Moses and Elijah, talking with him.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Peter said to Jesus, “Lord, it is good that we are here. If you wish, I will make three tents here, one for you and one for Moses and one for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23704F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23704F\"></sup>Elijah.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He was still speaking when, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23705G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23705G\"></sup>a bright cloud overshadowed them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23705H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23705H\"></sup>a voice from the cloud said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23705I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23705I\"></sup>“This is my beloved Son, with whom I am well pleased; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23705J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23705J\"></sup>listen to him.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23706K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23706K\"></sup>the disciples heard this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23706L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23706L\"></sup>they fell on their faces and were terrified.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But Jesus came and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23707M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23707M\"></sup>touched them, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“Rise, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23707N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23707N\"></sup>have no fear.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And when they lifted up their eyes, they saw no one but Jesus only.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23709O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23709O\"></sup>And as they were coming down the mountain, Jesus commanded them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23709P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23709P\"></sup>“Tell no one the vision, until the Son of Man is raised from the dead.”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And the disciples asked him, “Then why do the scribes say <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23710Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23710Q\"></sup>that first Elijah must come?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He answered, <span class=\"woj\">“Elijah does come, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23711R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23711R\"></sup>he will restore all things.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But I tell you that Elijah has already come, and they did not recognize him, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23712S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23712S\"></sup>did to him whatever they pleased. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23712T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23712T\"></sup>So also the Son of Man will certainly suffer at their hands.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23713U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23713U\"></sup>Then the disciples understood that he was speaking to them of John the Baptist.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23714V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23714V\"></sup>And when they came to the crowd, a man came up to him and, kneeling before him,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>said, “Lord, have mercy on my son, for he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23715W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23715W\"></sup>seizures and he suffers terribly. For often he falls into the fire, and often into the water.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And I brought him to your disciples, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23716X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23716X\"></sup>they could not heal him.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“O faithless and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23717Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23717Y\"></sup>twisted generation, how long am I to be with you? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23717Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23717Z\"></sup>How long am I to bear with you? Bring him here to me.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23718AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23718AA\"></sup>rebuked the demon, and it came out of him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23718AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23718AB\"></sup>the boy was healed instantly.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then the disciples came to Jesus privately and said, “Why could we not cast it out?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23720AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23720AC\"></sup>“Because of your little faith. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23720AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23720AD\"></sup>truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23720AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23720AE\"></sup>if you have faith like a grain of mustard seed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23720AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23720AF\"></sup>you will say to this mountain, ‘Move from here to there,’ and it will move, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23720AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23720AG\"></sup>nothing will be impossible for you.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23721AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23721AH\"></sup>As they were gathering in Galilee, Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“The Son of Man is about to be delivered into the hands of men,</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and they will kill him, and he will be raised on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23722AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23722AI\"></sup>the third day.”</span> And they were greatly distressed.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23723AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23723AJ\"></sup>When they came to Capernaum, the collectors of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23723AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23723AK\"></sup>the two-drachma tax went up to Peter and said, “Does your teacher not pay the tax?”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He said, “Yes.” And when he came into the house, Jesus spoke to him first, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23724AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23724AL\"></sup>“What do you think, Simon? From whom do kings of the earth take toll or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23724AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23724AM\"></sup>tax? From their sons or from others?”</span>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And when he said, “From others,” Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Then the sons are free.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>However, not to give offense to them, go to the sea and cast a hook and take the first fish that comes up, and when you open its mouth you will find a shekel. Take that and give it to them for me and for yourself.”</span>"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23727A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23727A\"></sup>At that time the disciples came to Jesus, saying, “Who is the greatest in the kingdom of heaven?”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And calling to him a child, he put him in the midst of them",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I say to you, unless you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23729B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23729B\"></sup>turn and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23729C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23729C\"></sup>become like children, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23729D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23729D\"></sup>will never enter the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23730E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23730E\"></sup>Whoever humbles himself like this child is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23730F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23730F\"></sup>greatest in the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23731G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23731G\"></sup>“Whoever receives one such child in my name receives me,</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23732H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23732H\"></sup>whoever causes one of these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23732I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23732I\"></sup>little ones who believe in me to sin, it would be better for him to have a great millstone fastened around his neck and to be drowned in the depth of the sea.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Woe to the world for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23733J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23733J\"></sup>temptations to sin! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23733K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23733K\"></sup>For it is necessary that temptations come, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23733L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23733L\"></sup>but woe to the one by whom the temptation comes!</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23734M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23734M\"></sup>And if your hand or your foot causes you to sin, cut it off and throw it away. It is better for you to enter life crippled or lame than with two hands or two feet to be thrown into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23734N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23734N\"></sup>the eternal fire.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23735O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23735O\"></sup>And if your eye causes you to sin, tear it out and throw it away. It is better for you to enter life with one eye than with two eyes to be thrown into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23735P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23735P\"></sup>hell of fire.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“See that you do not despise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23736Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23736Q\"></sup>one of these little ones. For I tell you that in heaven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23736R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23736R\"></sup>their angels always <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23736S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23736S\"></sup>see the face of my Father who is in heaven.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23737T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23737T\"></sup>What do you think? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23737U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23737U\"></sup>If a man has a hundred sheep, and one of them has gone astray, does he not leave the ninety-nine on the mountains and go in search of the one that went astray?</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And if he finds it, truly, I say to you, he rejoices over it more than over the ninety-nine that never went astray.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23739V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23739V\"></sup>it is not the will of my Father who is in heaven that one of these little ones should perish.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23740W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23740W\"></sup>“If your brother sins against you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23740X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23740X\"></sup>go and tell him his fault, between you and him alone. If he listens to you, you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23740Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23740Y\"></sup>gained your brother.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But if he does not listen, take one or two others along with you, that every charge may be established <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23741Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23741Z\"></sup>by the evidence of two or three witnesses.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If he refuses to listen to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23742AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23742AA\"></sup>tell it to the church. And if he refuses to listen even to the church, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23742AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23742AB\"></sup>let him be to you as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23742AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23742AC\"></sup>a Gentile and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23742AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23742AD\"></sup>a tax collector.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23743AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23743AE\"></sup>whatever you bind on earth shall be bound in heaven, and whatever you loose on earth shall be loosed in heaven.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Again I say to you, if two of you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23744AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23744AF\"></sup>agree on earth about anything they ask, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23744AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23744AG\"></sup>it will be done for them by my Father in heaven.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For where two or three are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23745AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23745AH\"></sup>gathered in my name, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23745AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23745AI\"></sup>there am I among them.”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then Peter came up and said to him, “Lord, how often <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23746AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23746AJ\"></sup>will my brother sin against me, and I forgive him? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23746AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23746AK\"></sup>As many as seven times?”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“I do not say to you seven times, but seventy-seven times.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Therefore the kingdom of heaven may be compared to a king who wished <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23748AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23748AL\"></sup>to settle accounts with his servants.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When he began to settle, one was brought to him who owed him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23749AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23749AM\"></sup>ten thousand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23749AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23749AN\"></sup>talents.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23750AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23750AO\"></sup>And since he could not pay, his master ordered him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23750AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23750AP\"></sup>to be sold, with his wife and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23750AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23750AQ\"></sup>children and all that he had, and payment to be made.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>So the servant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23751AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23751AR\"></sup>fell on his knees, imploring him, ‘Have patience with me, and I will pay you everything.’</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And out of pity for him, the master of that servant released him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23752AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23752AS\"></sup>forgave him the debt.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But when that same servant went out, he found one of his fellow servants who owed him a hundred <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23753AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23753AT\"></sup>denarii, and seizing him, he began to choke him, saying, ‘Pay what you owe.’</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>So his fellow servant fell down and pleaded with him, ‘Have patience with me, and I will pay you.’</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>He refused and went and put him in prison until he should pay the debt.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>When his fellow servants saw what had taken place, they were greatly distressed, and they went and reported to their master all that had taken place.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Then his master summoned him and said to him, ‘You wicked servant! I forgave you all that debt because you pleaded with me.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23758AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23758AU\"></sup>And should not you have had mercy on your fellow servant, as I had mercy on you?’</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23759AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23759AV\"></sup>And in anger his master delivered him to the jailers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23759AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23759AW\"></sup>until he should pay all his debt.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23760AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23760AX\"></sup>So also my heavenly Father will do to every one of you, if you do not forgive your brother <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23760AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23760AY\"></sup>from your heart.”</span>"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>Now when Jesus had finished these sayings, he went away from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23761A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23761A\"></sup>Galilee and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23761B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23761B\"></sup>entered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23761C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23761C\"></sup>the region of Judea beyond the Jordan.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23762D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23762D\"></sup>large crowds followed him, and he healed them there.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And Pharisees came up to him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23763E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23763E\"></sup>tested him by asking, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23763F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23763F\"></sup>“Is it lawful to divorce one's wife for any cause?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He answered, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23764G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23764G\"></sup>“Have you not read that he who created them from the beginning made them male and female,</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23765H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23765H\"></sup>‘Therefore a man shall leave his father and his mother and hold fast to his wife, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23765I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23765I\"></sup>the two shall become one flesh’?</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So they are no longer two but one flesh. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23766J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23766J\"></sup>What therefore God has joined together, let not man separate.”</span>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23767K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23767K\"></sup>“Why then did Moses command one to give a certificate of divorce and to send her away?”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Because of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23768L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23768L\"></sup>hardness of heart Moses allowed you to divorce your wives, but from the beginning it was not so.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23769M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23769M\"></sup>And I say to you: whoever divorces his wife, except for sexual immorality, and marries another, commits adultery.”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The disciples said to him, “If such is the case of a man with his wife, it is better not to marry.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23771N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23771N\"></sup>“Not everyone can receive this saying, but only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23771O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23771O\"></sup>those to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23771P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23771P\"></sup>whom it is given.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For there are eunuchs who have been so from birth, and there are eunuchs who have been made eunuchs by men, and there are eunuchs who have made themselves eunuchs <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23772Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23772Q\"></sup>for the sake of the kingdom of heaven. Let the one who is able to receive this receive it.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23773R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23773R\"></sup>Then children were brought to him that he might lay his hands on them and pray. The disciples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23773S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23773S\"></sup>rebuked the people,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>but Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23774T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23774T\"></sup>“Let the little children <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23774U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23774U\"></sup>come to me and do not hinder them, for to such belongs the kingdom of heaven.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And he laid his hands on them and went away.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23776V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23776V\"></sup>And behold, a man came up to him, saying, “Teacher, what good deed must I do to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23776W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23776W\"></sup>have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23776X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23776X\"></sup>eternal life?”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Why do you ask me about what is good? There is only one who is good. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23777Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23777Y\"></sup>If you would enter life, keep the commandments.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He said to him, “Which ones?” And Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23778Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23778Z\"></sup>“You shall not murder, You shall not commit adultery, You shall not steal, You shall not bear false witness,</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Honor your father and mother, and, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23779AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23779AA\"></sup>You shall love your neighbor as yourself.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The young man said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23780AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23780AB\"></sup>“All these I have kept. What do I still lack?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“If you would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23781AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23781AC\"></sup>perfect, go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23781AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23781AD\"></sup>sell what you possess and give to the poor, and you will have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23781AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23781AE\"></sup>treasure in heaven; and come, follow me.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23782AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23782AF\"></sup>When the young man heard this he went away sorrowful, for he had great possessions.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And Jesus said to his disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23783AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23783AG\"></sup>only with difficulty will a rich person enter the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23784AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23784AH\"></sup>Again I tell you, it is easier for a camel to go through the eye of a needle than for a rich person to enter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23784AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23784AI\"></sup>the kingdom of God.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When the disciples heard this, they were greatly astonished, saying, “Who then can be saved?”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23786AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23786AJ\"></sup>looked at them and said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23786AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23786AK\"></sup>“With man this is impossible, but with God all things are possible.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then Peter said in reply, “See, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23787AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23787AL\"></sup>we have left everything and followed you. What then will we have?”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I say to you, in the new world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23788AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23788AM\"></sup>when the Son of Man will sit on his glorious throne, you who have followed me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23788AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23788AN\"></sup>will also sit on twelve thrones, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23788AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23788AO\"></sup>judging the twelve tribes of Israel.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23789AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23789AP\"></sup>And everyone who has left houses or brothers or sisters or father or mother or children or lands, for my name's sake, will receive a hundredfold and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23789AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23789AQ\"></sup>inherit eternal life.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23790AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23790AR\"></sup>many who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23790AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23790AS\"></sup>first will be last, and the last first.</span>"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>“For the kingdom of heaven is like a master of a house who went out early in the morning to hire laborers for his vineyard.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>After agreeing with the laborers for a denarius a day, he sent them into his vineyard.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And going out about the third hour he saw others standing idle in the marketplace,</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and to them he said, ‘You go into the vineyard too, and whatever is right I will give you.’</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So they went.</span> <span class=\"woj\">Going out again about the sixth hour and the ninth hour, he did the same.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23796A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23796A\"></sup>about the eleventh hour he went out and found others standing. And he said to them, ‘Why do you stand here idle all day?’</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They said to him, ‘Because no one has hired us.’ He said to them, ‘You go into the vineyard too.’</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23798B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23798B\"></sup>when evening came, the owner of the vineyard said to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23798C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23798C\"></sup>foreman, ‘Call the laborers and pay them their wages, beginning with the last, up to the first.’</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And when those hired about the eleventh hour came, each of them received a denarius.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Now when those hired first came, they thought they would receive more, but each of them also received a denarius.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And on receiving it they grumbled at the master of the house,</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>saying, ‘These last worked only one hour, and you have made them equal to us who have borne the burden of the day and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23802D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23802D\"></sup>the scorching heat.’</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But he replied to one of them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23803E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23803E\"></sup>‘Friend, I am doing you no wrong. Did you not agree with me for a denarius?</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23804F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23804F\"></sup>what belongs to you and go. I choose to give to this last worker as I give to you.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23805G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23805G\"></sup>Am I not allowed to do what I choose with what belongs to me? Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23805H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23805H\"></sup>do you begrudge my generosity?’</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23806I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23806I\"></sup>the last will be first, and the first last.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23807J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23807J\"></sup>And as Jesus was going up to Jerusalem, he took the twelve disciples aside, and on the way he said to them,",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“See, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23808K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23808K\"></sup>we are going up to Jerusalem. And the Son of Man will be delivered over to the chief priests and scribes, and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23808L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23808L\"></sup>condemn him to death</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23809M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23809M\"></sup>deliver him over to the Gentiles <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23809N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23809N\"></sup>to be mocked and flogged and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23809O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23809O\"></sup>crucified, and he will be raised on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23809P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23809P\"></sup>the third day.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23810Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23810Q\"></sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23810R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23810R\"></sup>the mother of the sons of Zebedee came up to him with her sons, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23810S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23810S\"></sup>kneeling before him she asked him for something.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And he said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“What do you want?”</span> She said to him, “Say that these two sons of mine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23811T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23811T\"></sup>are to sit, one at your right hand and one at your left, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23811U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23811U\"></sup>in your kingdom.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23812V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23812V\"></sup>“You do not know what you are asking. Are you able <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23812W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23812W\"></sup>to drink the cup that I am to drink?”</span> They said to him, “We are able.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23813X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23813X\"></sup>“You will drink <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23813Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23813Y\"></sup>my cup, but to sit at my right hand and at my left is not mine to grant, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23813Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23813Z\"></sup>but it is for those for whom it has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23813AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23813AA\"></sup>prepared by my Father.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And when the ten heard it, they were indignant at the two brothers.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But Jesus called them to him and said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23815AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23815AB\"></sup>“You know that the rulers of the Gentiles <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23815AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23815AC\"></sup>lord it over them, and their great ones exercise authority over them.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23816AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23816AD\"></sup>It shall not be so among you. But whoever would be great among you must be your servant,</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>and whoever would be first among you must be your slave,</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>even as the Son of Man came not to be served but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23818AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23818AE\"></sup>to serve, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23818AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23818AF\"></sup>to give his life as a ransom for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23818AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23818AG\"></sup>many.”</span>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23819AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23819AH\"></sup>And as they went out of Jericho, a great crowd followed him.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And behold, there were two blind men sitting by the roadside, and when they heard that Jesus was passing by, they cried out, “Lord, have mercy on us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23820AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23820AI\"></sup>Son of David!”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The crowd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23821AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23821AJ\"></sup>rebuked them, telling them to be silent, but they cried out all the more, “Lord, have mercy on us, Son of David!”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And stopping, Jesus called them and said, <span class=\"woj\">“What do you want me to do for you?”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>They said to him, “Lord, let our eyes be opened.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And Jesus in pity touched their eyes, and immediately they recovered their sight and followed him."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23825A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23825A\"></sup>Now when they drew near to Jerusalem and came to Bethphage, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23825B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23825B\"></sup>the Mount of Olives, then Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23825C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23825C\"></sup>sent two disciples,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>saying to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Go into the village in front of you, and immediately you will find a donkey tied, and a colt with her. Untie them and bring them to me.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If anyone says anything to you, you shall say, ‘The Lord needs them,’ and he will send them at once.”</span>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>This took place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23828D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23828D\"></sup>to fulfill what was spoken by the prophet, saying,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23829E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23829E\"></sup>“Say to the daughter of Zion,‘Behold, your king is coming to you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23829F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23829F\"></sup>humble, and mounted on a donkey,on a colt, the foal of a beast of burden.’”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The disciples went and did as Jesus had directed them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They brought the donkey and the colt and put on them their cloaks, and he sat on them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Most of the crowd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23832G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23832G\"></sup>spread their cloaks on the road, and others cut branches from the trees and spread them on the road.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And the crowds that went before him and that followed him were shouting, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23833H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23833H\"></sup>“Hosanna to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23833I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23833I\"></sup>the Son of David! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23833J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23833J\"></sup>Blessed is he who comes in the name of the Lord! Hosanna <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23833K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23833K\"></sup>in the highest!”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23834L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23834L\"></sup>when he entered Jerusalem, the whole city was stirred up, saying, “Who is this?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the crowds said, “This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23835M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23835M\"></sup>the prophet Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23835N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23835N\"></sup>from Nazareth of Galilee.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23836O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23836O\"></sup>And Jesus entered the temple and drove out all who sold and bought in the temple, and he overturned the tables of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23836P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23836P\"></sup>the money-changers and the seats of those who sold <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23836Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23836Q\"></sup>pigeons.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“It is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23837R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23837R\"></sup>‘My house shall be called a house of prayer,’ but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23837S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23837S\"></sup>you make it a den of robbers.”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23838T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23838T\"></sup>And the blind and the lame came to him in the temple, and he healed them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23839U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23839U\"></sup>But when the chief priests and the scribes saw the wonderful things that he did, and the children crying out in the temple, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23839V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23839V\"></sup>“Hosanna to the Son of David!” they were indignant,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and they said to him, “Do you hear what these are saying?” And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Yes; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23840W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23840W\"></sup>have you never read,</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23840X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23840X\"></sup>“‘Out of the mouth of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23840Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23840Y\"></sup>infants and nursing babies</span><span class=\"woj\">you have prepared praise’?”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23841Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23841Z\"></sup>leaving them, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23841AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23841AA\"></sup>went out of the city to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23841AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23841AB\"></sup>Bethany and lodged there.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23842AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23842AC\"></sup>In the morning, as he was returning to the city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23842AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23842AD\"></sup>he became hungry.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23843AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23843AE\"></sup>And seeing a fig tree by the wayside, he went to it and found nothing on it but only leaves. And he said to it, <span class=\"woj\">“May no fruit ever come from you again!”</span> And the fig tree withered at once.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>When the disciples saw it, they marveled, saying, “How did the fig tree wither at once?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23845AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23845AF\"></sup>“Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23845AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23845AG\"></sup>if you have faith and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23845AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23845AH\"></sup>do not doubt, you will not only do what has been done to the fig tree, but even if you say to this mountain, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23845AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23845AI\"></sup>‘Be taken up and thrown into the sea,’ it will happen.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23846AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23846AJ\"></sup>whatever you ask in prayer, you will receive, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23846AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23846AK\"></sup>if you have faith.”</span>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23847AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23847AL\"></sup>And when he entered the temple, the chief priests and the elders of the people came up to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23847AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23847AM\"></sup>as he was teaching, and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23847AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23847AN\"></sup>“By what authority are you doing these things, and who gave you this authority?”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“I also will ask you one question, and if you tell me the answer, then I also will tell you by what authority I do these things.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The baptism of John, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23849AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23849AO\"></sup>from where did it come? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23849AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23849AP\"></sup>From heaven or from man?”</span> And they discussed it among themselves, saying, “If we say, ‘From heaven,’ he will say to us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23849AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23849AQ\"></sup>‘Why then did you not believe him?’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But if we say, ‘From man,’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23850AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23850AR\"></sup>we are afraid of the crowd, for they all hold that John was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23850AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23850AS\"></sup>a prophet.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>So they answered Jesus, “We do not know.” And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Neither will I tell you by what authority I do these things.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23852AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23852AT\"></sup>“What do you think? A man had two sons. And he went to the first and said, ‘Son, go and work in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23852AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23852AU\"></sup>the vineyard today.’</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And he answered, ‘I will not,’ but afterward he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23853AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23853AV\"></sup>changed his mind and went.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And he went to the other son and said the same. And he answered, ‘I go, sir,’ but did not go.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Which of the two did the will of his father?”</span> They said, “The first.” Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23855AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23855AW\"></sup>the tax collectors and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23855AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23855AX\"></sup>the prostitutes go into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23855AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23855AY\"></sup>the kingdom of God before you.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For John came to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23856AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23856AZ\"></sup>in the way of righteousness, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23856BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23856BA\"></sup>you did not believe him, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23856BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23856BB\"></sup>the tax collectors and the prostitutes believed him. And even when you saw it, you did not afterward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23856BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23856BC\"></sup>change your minds and believe him.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23857BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23857BD\"></sup>“Hear another parable. There was a master of a house who planted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23857BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23857BE\"></sup>a vineyard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23857BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23857BF\"></sup>and put a fence around it and dug a winepress in it and built a tower and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23857BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23857BG\"></sup>leased it to tenants, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23857BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23857BH\"></sup>went into another country.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>When the season for fruit drew near, he sent his servants to the tenants <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23858BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23858BI\"></sup>to get his fruit.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23859BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23859BJ\"></sup>And the tenants took his servants and beat one, killed another, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23859BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23859BK\"></sup>stoned another.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23860BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23860BL\"></sup>Again he sent other servants, more than the first. And they did the same to them.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Finally he sent his son to them, saying, ‘They will respect my son.’</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>But when the tenants saw the son, they said to themselves, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23862BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23862BM\"></sup>‘This is the heir. Come, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23862BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23862BN\"></sup>let us kill him and have his inheritance.’</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And they took him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23863BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23863BO\"></sup>threw him out of the vineyard and killed him.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23864BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23864BP\"></sup>When therefore the owner of the vineyard comes, what will he do to those tenants?”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>They said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23865BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23865BQ\"></sup>“He will put those wretches to a miserable death and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23865BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23865BR\"></sup>let out the vineyard to other tenants who will give him the fruits in their seasons.”",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23866BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23866BS\"></sup>“Have you never read in the Scriptures:</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23866BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23866BT\"></sup>“‘The stone that the builders rejected</span><span class=\"woj\">has become the cornerstone;</span><span class=\"woj\">this was the Lord's doing,</span><span class=\"woj\">and it is marvelous in our eyes’?</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Therefore I tell you, the kingdom of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23867BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23867BU\"></sup>will be taken away from you and given to a people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23867BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23867BV\"></sup>producing its fruits.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23868BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23868BW\"></sup>the one who falls on this stone will be broken to pieces; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23868BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23868BX\"></sup>when it falls on anyone, it will crush him.”</span>",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>When the chief priests and the Pharisees heard his parables, they perceived that he was speaking about them.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23870BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23870BY\"></sup>although they were seeking to arrest him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23870BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23870BZ\"></sup>they feared the crowds, because they held him to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23870CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23870CA\"></sup>a prophet."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>And again Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23871A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23871A\"></sup>spoke to them in parables, saying,",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23872B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23872B\"></sup>“The kingdom of heaven may be compared to a king who gave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23872C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23872C\"></sup>a wedding feast for his son,</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23873D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23873D\"></sup>sent his servants to call those who were invited to the wedding feast, but they would not come.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23874E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23874E\"></sup>Again he sent other servants, saying, ‘Tell those who are invited, “See, I have prepared my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23874F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23874F\"></sup>dinner, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23874G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23874G\"></sup>my oxen and my fat calves have been slaughtered, and everything is ready. Come to the wedding feast.”’</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23875H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23875H\"></sup>they paid no attention and went off, one to his farm, another to his business,</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>while the rest seized his servants, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23876I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23876I\"></sup>treated them shamefully, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23876J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23876J\"></sup>killed them.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The king was angry, and he sent his troops and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23877K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23877K\"></sup>destroyed those murderers and burned their city.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then he said to his servants, ‘The wedding feast is ready, but those invited were not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23878L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23878L\"></sup>worthy.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Go therefore to the main roads and invite to the wedding feast as many as you find.’</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And those servants went out into the roads and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23880M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23880M\"></sup>gathered all whom they found, both bad and good. So the wedding hall was filled with guests.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“But when the king came in to look at the guests, he saw there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23881N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23881N\"></sup>a man who had no wedding garment.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And he said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23882O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23882O\"></sup>‘Friend, how did you get in here without a wedding garment?’ And he was speechless.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then the king said to the attendants, ‘Bind him hand and foot and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23883P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23883P\"></sup>cast him into the outer darkness. In that place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23883Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23883Q\"></sup>there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth.’</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For many are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23884R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23884R\"></sup>called, but few are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23884S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23884S\"></sup>chosen.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23885T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23885T\"></sup>Then the Pharisees went and plotted how <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23885U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23885U\"></sup>to entangle him in his words.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And they sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23886V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23886V\"></sup>their disciples to him, along with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23886W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23886W\"></sup>the Herodians, saying, “Teacher, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23886X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23886X\"></sup>we know that you are true and teach <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23886Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23886Y\"></sup>the way of God truthfully, and you do not care about anyone's opinion, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23886Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23886Z\"></sup>you are not swayed by appearances.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Tell us, then, what you think. Is it lawful to pay <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23887AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23887AA\"></sup>taxes to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23887AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23887AB\"></sup>Caesar, or not?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But Jesus, aware of their malice, said, <span class=\"woj\">“Why <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23888AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23888AC\"></sup>put me to the test, you hypocrites?</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Show me the coin for the tax.”</span> And they brought him a denarius.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Whose likeness and inscription is this?”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They said, “Caesar's.” Then he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23891AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23891AD\"></sup>“Therefore render to Caesar the things that are Caesar's, and to God the things that are God's.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>When they heard it, they marveled. And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23892AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23892AE\"></sup>left him and went away.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The same day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23893AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23893AF\"></sup>Sadducees came to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23893AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23893AG\"></sup>who say that there is no resurrection, and they asked him a question,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>saying, “Teacher, Moses said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23894AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23894AH\"></sup>‘If a man dies having no children, his brother must marry the widow and raise up offspring for his brother.’",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now there were seven brothers among us. The first married and died, and having no offspring left his wife to his brother.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>So too the second and third, down to the seventh.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>After them all, the woman died.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>In the resurrection, therefore, of the seven, whose wife will she be? For they all had her.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“You are wrong, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23899AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23899AI\"></sup>because you know neither the Scriptures nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23899AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23899AJ\"></sup>the power of God.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For in the resurrection they neither <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23900AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23900AK\"></sup>marry nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23900AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23900AL\"></sup>are given in marriage, but are like angels in heaven.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And as for the resurrection of the dead, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23901AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23901AM\"></sup>have you not read what was said to you by God:</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23902AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23902AN\"></sup>‘I am the God of Abraham, and the God of Isaac, and the God of Jacob’? He is not God of the dead, but of the living.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And when the crowd heard it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23903AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23903AO\"></sup>they were astonished at his teaching.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23904AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23904AP\"></sup>But when the Pharisees heard that he had silenced <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23904AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23904AQ\"></sup>the Sadducees, they gathered together.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23905AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23905AR\"></sup>And one of them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23905AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23905AS\"></sup>a lawyer, asked him a question <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23905AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23905AT\"></sup>to test him.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“Teacher, which is the great commandment in the Law?”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And he said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23907AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23907AU\"></sup>“You shall love the Lord your God with all your heart and with all your soul and with all your mind.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>This is the great and first commandment.</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23909AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23909AV\"></sup>a second is like it: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23909AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23909AW\"></sup>You shall love your neighbor as yourself.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23910AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23910AX\"></sup>On these two commandments depend <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23910AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23910AY\"></sup>all the Law and the Prophets.”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23911AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23911AZ\"></sup>Now while the Pharisees <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23911BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23911BA\"></sup>were gathered together, Jesus asked them a question,",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>saying, <span class=\"woj\">“What do you think about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23912BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23912BB\"></sup>the Christ? Whose son is he?”</span> They said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23912BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23912BC\"></sup>“The son of David.”",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“How is it then that David, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23913BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23913BD\"></sup>in the Spirit, calls him Lord, saying,</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23914BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23914BE\"></sup>“‘The Lord said to my Lord,</span><span class=\"woj\">“Sit at my right hand,</span><span class=\"woj\">until I put your enemies under your feet”’?</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>If then David calls him Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23915BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23915BF\"></sup>how is he his son?”</span>",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23916BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23916BG\"></sup>And no one was able to answer him a word, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23916BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23916BH\"></sup>nor from that day did anyone dare to ask him any more questions."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>Then Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23917A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23917A\"></sup>said to the crowds and to his disciples,",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23918B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23918B\"></sup>“The scribes and the Pharisees <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23918C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23918C\"></sup>sit on Moses' seat,</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>so do and observe whatever they tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23919D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23919D\"></sup>but not the works they do. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23919E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23919E\"></sup>For they preach, but do not practice.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23920F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23920F\"></sup>They tie up heavy burdens, hard to bear, and lay them on people's shoulders, but they themselves are not willing to move them with their finger.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23921G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23921G\"></sup>They do all their deeds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23921H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23921H\"></sup>to be seen by others. For they make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23921I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23921I\"></sup>their phylacteries broad and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23921J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23921J\"></sup>their fringes long,</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23922K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23922K\"></sup>love the place of honor at feasts and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23922L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23922L\"></sup>the best seats in the synagogues</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23923M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23923M\"></sup>greetings in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23923N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23923N\"></sup>the marketplaces and being called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23923O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23923O\"></sup>rabbi by others.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23924P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23924P\"></sup>But you are not to be called rabbi, for you have one teacher, and you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23924Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23924Q\"></sup>all brothers.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23925R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23925R\"></sup>And call no man your father on earth, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23925S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23925S\"></sup>you have one Father, who is in heaven.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Neither be called instructors, for you have one instructor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23926T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23926T\"></sup>the Christ.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23927U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23927U\"></sup>The greatest among you shall be your servant.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23928V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23928V\"></sup>Whoever exalts himself will be humbled, and whoever humbles himself will be exalted.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“But woe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23929W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23929W\"></sup>to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! For you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23929X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23929X\"></sup>shut the kingdom of heaven in people's faces. For you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23929Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23929Y\"></sup>neither enter yourselves nor allow those who would enter to go in.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! For you travel across sea and land to make a single <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23930Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23930Z\"></sup>proselyte, and when he becomes a proselyte, you make him twice as much a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23930AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23930AA\"></sup>child of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23930AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23930AB\"></sup>hell as yourselves.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Woe to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23931AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23931AC\"></sup>you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23931AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23931AD\"></sup>blind guides, who say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23931AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23931AE\"></sup>‘If anyone swears by the temple, it is nothing, but if anyone swears by the gold of the temple, he is bound by his oath.’</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You blind fools! For which is greater, the gold or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23932AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23932AF\"></sup>the temple that has made the gold sacred?</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And you say, ‘If anyone swears by the altar, it is nothing, but if anyone swears by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23933AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23933AG\"></sup>the gift that is on the altar, he is bound by his oath.’</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You blind men! For which is greater, the gift or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23934AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23934AH\"></sup>the altar that makes the gift sacred?</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So whoever swears by the altar swears by it and by everything on it.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And whoever swears by the temple swears by it and by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23936AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23936AI\"></sup>him who dwells in it.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And whoever swears by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23937AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23937AJ\"></sup>heaven swears by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23937AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23937AK\"></sup>the throne of God and by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23937AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23937AL\"></sup>him who sits upon it.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23938AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23938AM\"></sup>“Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23938AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23938AN\"></sup>you tithe mint and dill and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23938AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23938AO\"></sup>cumin, and have neglected the weightier matters of the law: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23938AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23938AP\"></sup>justice and mercy and faithfulness. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23938AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23938AQ\"></sup>These you ought to have done, without neglecting the others.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>You blind guides, straining out a gnat and swallowing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23939AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23939AR\"></sup>a camel!</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23940AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23940AS\"></sup>“Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23940AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23940AT\"></sup>you clean the outside of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23940AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23940AU\"></sup>the cup and the plate, but inside they are full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23940AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23940AV\"></sup>greed and self-indulgence.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>You blind Pharisee! First clean the inside of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23941AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23941AW\"></sup>the cup and the plate, that the outside also may be clean.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23942AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23942AX\"></sup>“Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! For you are like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23942AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23942AY\"></sup>whitewashed tombs, which outwardly appear beautiful, but within are full of dead people's bones and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23942AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23942AZ\"></sup>all uncleanness.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So you also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23943BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23943BA\"></sup>outwardly appear righteous to others, but within you are full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23943BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23943BB\"></sup>hypocrisy and lawlessness.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23944BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23944BC\"></sup>“Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! For you build the tombs of the prophets and decorate the monuments of the righteous,</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>saying, ‘If we had lived in the days of our fathers, we would not have taken part with them in shedding the blood of the prophets.’</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Thus you witness against yourselves that you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23946BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23946BD\"></sup>sons of those who murdered the prophets.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23947BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23947BE\"></sup>Fill up, then, the measure of your fathers.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>You serpents, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23948BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23948BF\"></sup>you brood of vipers, how are you to escape being sentenced to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23948BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23948BG\"></sup>hell?</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23949BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23949BH\"></sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23949BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23949BI\"></sup>I send you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23949BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23949BJ\"></sup>prophets and wise men and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23949BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23949BK\"></sup>scribes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23949BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23949BL\"></sup>some of whom you will kill and crucify, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23949BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23949BM\"></sup>some you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23949BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23949BN\"></sup>flog in your synagogues and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23949BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23949BO\"></sup>persecute from town to town,</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>so that on you may come all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23950BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23950BP\"></sup>the righteous blood shed on earth, from the blood of righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23950BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23950BQ\"></sup>Abel to the blood of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23950BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23950BR\"></sup>Zechariah the son of Barachiah, whom you murdered between <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23950BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23950BS\"></sup>the sanctuary and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23950BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23950BT\"></sup>the altar.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23951BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23951BU\"></sup>all these things will come upon this generation.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23952BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23952BV\"></sup>“O Jerusalem, Jerusalem, the city that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23952BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23952BW\"></sup>kills the prophets and stones those who are sent to it! How often would I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23952BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23952BX\"></sup>gathered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23952BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23952BY\"></sup>your children together <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23952BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23952BZ\"></sup>as a hen gathers her brood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23952CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23952CA\"></sup>under her wings, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23952CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23952CB\"></sup>you were not willing!</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>See, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23953CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23953CC\"></sup>your house is left to you desolate.</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>For I tell you, you will not see me again, until you say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23954CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23954CD\"></sup>‘Blessed is he who comes in the name of the Lord.’”</span>"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23955A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23955A\"></sup>Jesus left the temple and was going away, when his disciples came to point out to him the buildings of the temple.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But he answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“You see all these, do you not? Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23956B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23956B\"></sup>there will not be left here one stone upon another that will not be thrown down.”</span>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>As he sat on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23957C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23957C\"></sup>the Mount of Olives, the disciples came to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23957D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23957D\"></sup>privately, saying, “Tell us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23957E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23957E\"></sup>when will these things be, and what will be the sign of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23957F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23957F\"></sup>coming and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23957G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23957G\"></sup>the end of the age?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23958H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23958H\"></sup>“See that no one leads you astray.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23959I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23959I\"></sup>many will come in my name, saying, ‘I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23959J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23959J\"></sup>the Christ,’ and they will lead many astray.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And you will hear of wars and rumors of wars. See that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23960K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23960K\"></sup>are not alarmed, for this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23960L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23960L\"></sup>must take place, but the end is not yet.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23961M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23961M\"></sup>nation will rise against nation, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23961N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23961N\"></sup>kingdom against kingdom, and there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23961O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23961O\"></sup>famines and earthquakes in various places.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>All these are but the beginning of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23962P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23962P\"></sup>the birth pains.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23963Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23963Q\"></sup>they will deliver you up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23963R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23963R\"></sup>to tribulation and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23963S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23963S\"></sup>put you to death, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23963T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23963T\"></sup>you will be hated by all nations for my name's sake.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And then many will fall away and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23964U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23964U\"></sup>betray one another and hate one another.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23965V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23965V\"></sup>false prophets will arise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23965W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23965W\"></sup>and lead many astray.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And because lawlessness will be increased, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23966X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23966X\"></sup>the love of many will grow cold.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23967Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23967Y\"></sup>But the one who endures to the end will be saved.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And this gospel of the kingdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23968Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23968Z\"></sup>will be proclaimed throughout the whole world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23968AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23968AA\"></sup>as a testimony <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23968AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23968AB\"></sup>to all nations, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23968AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23968AC\"></sup>then the end will come.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“So when you see the abomination of desolation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23969AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23969AD\"></sup>spoken of by the prophet Daniel, standing in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23969AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23969AE\"></sup>the holy place (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23969AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23969AF\"></sup>let the reader understand),</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>then let those who are in Judea flee to the mountains.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23971AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23971AG\"></sup>Let the one who is on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23971AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23971AH\"></sup>the housetop not go down to take what is in his house,</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and let the one who is in the field not turn back to take his cloak.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23973AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23973AI\"></sup>alas for women who are pregnant and for those who are nursing infants in those days!</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Pray that your flight may not be in winter or on a Sabbath.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For then there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23975AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23975AJ\"></sup>great tribulation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23975AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23975AK\"></sup>such as has not been from the beginning of the world until now, no, and never will be.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And if those days had not been cut short, no human being would be saved. But for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23976AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23976AL\"></sup>the sake of the elect those days will be cut short.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23977AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23977AM\"></sup>Then if anyone says to you, ‘Look, here is the Christ!’ or ‘There he is!’ do not believe it.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23978AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23978AN\"></sup>false christs and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23978AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23978AO\"></sup>false prophets will arise and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23978AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23978AP\"></sup>perform great signs and wonders, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23978AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23978AQ\"></sup>so as to lead astray, if possible, even the elect.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>See, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23979AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23979AR\"></sup>I have told you beforehand.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>So, if they say to you, ‘Look, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23980AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23980AS\"></sup>he is in the wilderness,’ do not go out. If they say, ‘Look, he is in the inner rooms,’ do not believe it.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23981AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23981AT\"></sup>For as the lightning comes from the east and shines as far as the west, so will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23981AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23981AU\"></sup>the coming of the Son of Man.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23982AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23982AV\"></sup>Wherever the corpse is, there the vultures will gather.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Immediately after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23983AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23983AW\"></sup>the tribulation of those days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23983AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23983AX\"></sup>the sun will be darkened, and the moon will not give its light, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23983AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23983AY\"></sup>the stars will fall from heaven, and the powers of the heavens will be shaken.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23984AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23984AZ\"></sup>will appear in heaven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23984BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23984BA\"></sup>the sign of the Son of Man, and then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23984BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23984BB\"></sup>all the tribes of the earth will mourn, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23984BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23984BC\"></sup>they will see the Son of Man coming on the clouds of heaven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23984BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23984BD\"></sup>with power and great glory.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23985BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23985BE\"></sup>he will send out his angels with a loud <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23985BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23985BF\"></sup>trumpet call, and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23985BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23985BG\"></sup>gather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23985BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23985BH\"></sup>his elect from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23985BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23985BI\"></sup>the four winds, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23985BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23985BJ\"></sup>from one end of heaven to the other.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“From the fig tree learn its lesson: as soon as its branch becomes tender and puts out its leaves, you know that summer is near.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So also, when you see all these things, you know that he is near, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23987BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23987BK\"></sup>at the very gates.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23988BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23988BL\"></sup>Truly, I say to you, this generation will not pass away until all these things take place.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23989BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23989BM\"></sup>Heaven and earth will pass away, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23989BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23989BN\"></sup>my words will not pass away.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“But concerning that day and hour <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23990BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23990BO\"></sup>no one knows, not even the angels of heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23990BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23990BP\"></sup>nor the Son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23990BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23990BQ\"></sup>but the Father only.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23991BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23991BR\"></sup>For as were the days of Noah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23991BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23991BS\"></sup>so will be the coming of the Son of Man.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23992BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23992BT\"></sup>For as in those days before the flood they were eating and drinking, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23992BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23992BU\"></sup>marrying and giving in marriage, until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23992BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23992BV\"></sup>the day when Noah entered the ark,</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>and they were unaware until the flood came and swept them all away, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23993BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23993BW\"></sup>so will be the coming of the Son of Man.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Then two men will be in the field; one will be taken and one left.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23995BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23995BX\"></sup>Two women will be grinding <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23995BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23995BY\"></sup>at the mill; one will be taken and one left.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23996BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23996BZ\"></sup>stay awake, for you do not know on what day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23996CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23996CA\"></sup>your Lord is coming.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23997CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23997CB\"></sup>But know this, that if the master of the house had known in what part of the night <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23997CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23997CC\"></sup>the thief was coming, he would have stayed awake and would not have let his house be broken into.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Therefore you also must be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23998CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23998CD\"></sup>ready, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23998CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23998CE\"></sup>the Son of Man is coming at an hour you do not expect.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>“Who then is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23999CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23999CF\"></sup>the faithful and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23999CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23999CG\"></sup>wise servant, whom his master has set over his household, to give them their food at the proper time?</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24000CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24000CH\"></sup>Blessed is that servant whom his master will find so doing when he comes.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24001CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24001CI\"></sup>he will set him over all his possessions.</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>But if that wicked servant says to himself, ‘My master <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24002CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24002CJ\"></sup>is delayed,’</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>and begins to beat his fellow servants and eats and drinks with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24003CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24003CK\"></sup>drunkards,</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>the master of that servant will come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24004CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24004CL\"></sup>on a day when he does not expect him and at an hour he does not know</span>",
			"51": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>and will cut him in pieces and put him with the hypocrites. In that place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24005CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24005CM\"></sup>there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth.</span>"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>“Then the kingdom of heaven will be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24006A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24006A\"></sup>ten virgins who took their lamps and went to meet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24006B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24006B\"></sup>the bridegroom.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Five of them were foolish, and five were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24007C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24007C\"></sup>wise.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For when the foolish took their lamps, they took no oil with them,</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>but the wise took flasks of oil with their lamps.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>As the bridegroom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24010D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24010D\"></sup>was delayed, they all became drowsy and slept.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24011E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24011E\"></sup>at midnight there was a cry, ‘Here is the bridegroom! Come out to meet him.’</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then all those virgins rose and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24012F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24012F\"></sup>trimmed their lamps.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the foolish said to the wise, ‘Give us some of your oil, for our lamps are going out.’</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But the wise answered, saying, ‘Since there will not be enough for us and for you, go rather to the dealers and buy for yourselves.’</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And while they were going to buy, the bridegroom came, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24015G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24015G\"></sup>those who were ready went in with him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24015H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24015H\"></sup>the marriage feast, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24015I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24015I\"></sup>the door was shut.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Afterward the other virgins came also, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24016J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24016J\"></sup>‘Lord, lord, open to us.’</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24017K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24017K\"></sup>But he answered, ‘Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24017L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24017L\"></sup>I do not know you.’</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24018M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24018M\"></sup>Watch therefore, for you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24018N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24018N\"></sup>know neither the day nor the hour.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24019O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24019O\"></sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24019P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24019P\"></sup>it will be like a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24019Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24019Q\"></sup>going on a journey, who called his servants and entrusted to them his property.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>To one he gave five <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24020R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24020R\"></sup>talents, to another two, to another one, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24020S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24020S\"></sup>to each according to his ability. Then he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24020T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24020T\"></sup>went away.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He who had received the five talents went at once and traded with them, and he made five talents more.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So also he who had the two talents made two talents more.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But he who had received the one talent went and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24023U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24023U\"></sup>dug in the ground and hid his master's money.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24024V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24024V\"></sup>after a long time the master of those servants came and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24024W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24024W\"></sup>settled accounts with them.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And he who had received the five talents came forward, bringing five talents more, saying, ‘Master, you delivered to me five talents; here, I have made five talents more.’</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>His master said to him, ‘Well done, good and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24026X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24026X\"></sup>faithful servant. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24026Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24026Y\"></sup>You have been faithful over a little; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24026Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24026Z\"></sup>I will set you over much. Enter into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24026AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24026AA\"></sup>the joy of your master.’</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And he also who had the two talents came forward, saying, ‘Master, you delivered to me two talents; here, I have made two talents more.’</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>His master said to him, ‘Well done, good and faithful servant. You have been faithful over a little; I will set you over much. Enter into the joy of your master.’</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He also who had received the one talent came forward, saying, ‘Master, I knew you to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24029AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24029AB\"></sup>a hard man, reaping <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24029AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24029AC\"></sup>where you did not sow, and gathering where you scattered no seed,</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>so I was afraid, and I went and hid your talent in the ground. Here, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24030AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24030AD\"></sup>you have what is yours.’</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But his master answered him, ‘You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24031AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24031AE\"></sup>wicked and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24031AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24031AF\"></sup>slothful servant! You knew that I reap where I have not sown and gather where I scattered no seed?</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then you ought to have invested my money with the bankers, and at my coming I should have received what was my own with interest.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So take the talent from him and give it to him who has the ten talents.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24034AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24034AG\"></sup>For to everyone who has will more be given, and he will have an abundance. But from the one who has not, even what he has will be taken away.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24035AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24035AH\"></sup>cast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24035AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24035AI\"></sup>the worthless servant into the outer darkness. In that place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24035AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24035AJ\"></sup>there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth.’</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24036AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24036AK\"></sup>“When the Son of Man comes in his glory, and all the angels with him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24036AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24036AL\"></sup>then he will sit on his glorious throne.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Before him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24037AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24037AM\"></sup>will be gathered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24037AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24037AN\"></sup>all the nations, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24037AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24037AO\"></sup>he will separate people one from another as a shepherd separates <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24037AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24037AP\"></sup>the sheep from the goats.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And he will place the sheep on his right, but the goats on the left.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24039AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24039AQ\"></sup>the King will say to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24039AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24039AR\"></sup>those on his right, ‘Come, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24039AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24039AS\"></sup>who are blessed by my Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24039AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24039AT\"></sup>inherit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24039AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24039AU\"></sup>the kingdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24039AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24039AV\"></sup>prepared for you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24039AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24039AW\"></sup>from the foundation of the world.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24040AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24040AX\"></sup>I was hungry and you gave me food, I was thirsty and you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24040AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24040AY\"></sup>gave me drink, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24040AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24040AZ\"></sup>I was a stranger and you welcomed me,</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24041BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24041BA\"></sup>I was naked and you clothed me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24041BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24041BB\"></sup>I was sick and you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24041BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24041BC\"></sup>visited me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24041BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24041BD\"></sup>I was in prison and you came to me.’</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Then the righteous will answer him, saying, ‘Lord, when did we see you hungry and feed you, or thirsty and give you drink?</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And when did we see you a stranger and welcome you, or naked and clothe you?</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And when did we see you sick or in prison and visit you?’</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24045BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24045BE\"></sup>the King will answer them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24045BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24045BF\"></sup>‘Truly, I say to you, as you did it to one of the least of these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24045BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24045BG\"></sup>my brothers, you did it to me.’</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>“Then he will say to those on his left, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24046BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24046BH\"></sup>‘Depart from me, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24046BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24046BI\"></sup>cursed, into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24046BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24046BJ\"></sup>the eternal fire prepared for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24046BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24046BK\"></sup>the devil and his angels.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24047BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24047BL\"></sup>I was hungry and you gave me no food, I was thirsty and you gave me no drink,</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>I was a stranger and you did not welcome me, naked and you did not clothe me, sick and in prison and you did not visit me.’</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Then they also will answer, saying, ‘Lord, when did we see you hungry or thirsty or a stranger or naked or sick or in prison, and did not minister to you?’</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Then he will answer them, saying, ‘Truly, I say to you, as you did not do it to one of the least of these, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24050BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24050BM\"></sup>you did not do it to me.’</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>And these will go away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24051BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24051BN\"></sup>into eternal punishment, but the righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24051BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24051BO\"></sup>into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24051BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24051BP\"></sup>eternal life.”</span>"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>When Jesus had finished all these sayings, he said to his disciples,",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24053A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24053A\"></sup>“You know that after two days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24053B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24053B\"></sup>the Passover is coming, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24053C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24053C\"></sup>the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24053D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24053D\"></sup>will be delivered up to be crucified.”</span>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24054E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24054E\"></sup>Then the chief priests and the elders of the people gathered in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24054F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24054F\"></sup>the palace of the high priest, whose name was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24054G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24054G\"></sup>Caiaphas,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24055H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24055H\"></sup>and plotted together in order to arrest Jesus by stealth and kill him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But they said, “Not during the feast, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24056I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24056I\"></sup>lest there be an uproar among the people.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24057J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24057J\"></sup>Now when Jesus was at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24057K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24057K\"></sup>Bethany in the house of Simon the leper,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>a woman came up to him with an alabaster flask of very expensive ointment, and she poured it on his head as he reclined at table.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And when the disciples saw it, they were indignant, saying, “Why this waste?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For this could have been sold for a large sum and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24060L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24060L\"></sup>given to the poor.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24061M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24061M\"></sup>Jesus, aware of this, said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Why do you trouble the woman? For she has done a beautiful thing to me.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24062N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24062N\"></sup>you always have the poor with you, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24062O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24062O\"></sup>you will not always have me.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>In pouring this ointment on my body, she has done it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24063P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24063P\"></sup>to prepare me for burial.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Truly, I say to you, wherever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24064Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24064Q\"></sup>this gospel is proclaimed in the whole world, what she has done will also be told <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24064R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24064R\"></sup>in memory of her.”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24065S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24065S\"></sup>Then one of the twelve, whose name was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24065T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24065T\"></sup>Judas Iscariot, went to the chief priests",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and said, “What will you give me if I deliver him over to you?” And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24066U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24066U\"></sup>paid him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24066V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24066V\"></sup>thirty pieces of silver.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And from that moment he sought an opportunity <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24067W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24067W\"></sup>to betray him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24068X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24068X\"></sup>Now on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24068Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24068Y\"></sup>the first day of Unleavened Bread the disciples came to Jesus, saying, “Where will you have us prepare for you to eat the Passover?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He said, <span class=\"woj\">“Go into the city to a certain man and say to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24069Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24069Z\"></sup>‘The Teacher says, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24069AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24069AA\"></sup>My time is at hand. I will keep the Passover at your house with my disciples.’”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And the disciples did as Jesus had directed them, and they prepared the Passover.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24071AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24071AB\"></sup>When it was evening, he reclined at table with the twelve.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And as they were eating, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24072AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24072AC\"></sup>he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I say to you, one of you will betray me.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And they were very sorrowful and began to say to him one after another, “Is it I, Lord?”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He answered, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24074AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24074AD\"></sup>“He who has dipped his hand in the dish with me will betray me.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The Son of Man goes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24075AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24075AE\"></sup>as it is written of him, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24075AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24075AF\"></sup>woe to that man by whom the Son of Man is betrayed! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24075AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24075AG\"></sup>It would have been better for that man if he had not been born.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Judas, who would betray him, answered, “Is it I, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24076AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24076AH\"></sup>Rabbi?” He said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24076AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24076AI\"></sup>“You have said so.”</span>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24077AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24077AJ\"></sup>Now as they were eating, Jesus took bread, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24077AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24077AK\"></sup>after blessing it broke it and gave it to the disciples, and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Take, eat; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24077AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24077AL\"></sup>this is my body.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And he took a cup, and when he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24078AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24078AM\"></sup>had given thanks he gave it to them, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“Drink of it, all of you,</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24079AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24079AN\"></sup>this is my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24079AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24079AO\"></sup>blood of the covenant, which is poured out for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24079AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24079AP\"></sup>many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24079AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24079AQ\"></sup>for the forgiveness of sins.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I tell you I will not drink again of this fruit of the vine until that day when I drink it new with you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24080AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24080AR\"></sup>in my Father's kingdom.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24081AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24081AS\"></sup>And when they had sung a hymn, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24081AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24081AT\"></sup>they went out to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24081AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24081AU\"></sup>the Mount of Olives.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Then Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“You will all fall away because of me this night. For it is written, ‘I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24082AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24082AV\"></sup>strike the shepherd, and the sheep of the flock will be scattered.’</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>But after I am raised up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24083AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24083AW\"></sup>I will go before you to Galilee.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24084AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24084AX\"></sup>Peter answered him, “Though they all fall away because of you, I will never fall away.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24085AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24085AY\"></sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I tell you, this very night, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24085AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24085AZ\"></sup>before the rooster crows, you will deny me three times.”</span>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24086BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24086BA\"></sup>Peter said to him, “Even if I must die with you, I will not deny you!” And all the disciples said the same.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24087BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24087BB\"></sup>Then Jesus went with them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24087BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24087BC\"></sup>to a place called Gethsemane, and he said to his disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“Sit here, while I go over there and pray.”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And taking with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24088BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24088BD\"></sup>Peter and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24088BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24088BE\"></sup>the two sons of Zebedee, he began to be sorrowful and troubled.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Then he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24089BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24089BF\"></sup>“My soul is very sorrowful, even to death; remain here, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24089BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24089BG\"></sup>watch with me.”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And going a little farther he fell on his face <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24090BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24090BH\"></sup>and prayed, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“My Father, if it be possible, let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24090BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24090BI\"></sup>this cup pass from me; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24090BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24090BJ\"></sup>nevertheless, not as I will, but as you will.”</span>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And he came to the disciples and found them sleeping. And he said to Peter, <span class=\"woj\">“So, could you not watch with me one hour?</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24092BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24092BK\"></sup>Watch and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24092BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24092BL\"></sup>pray that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24092BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24092BM\"></sup>may not enter into temptation. The spirit indeed is willing, but the flesh is weak.”</span>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Again, for the second time, he went away and prayed, <span class=\"woj\">“My Father, if this cannot pass unless I drink it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24093BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24093BN\"></sup>your will be done.”</span>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And again he came and found them sleeping, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24094BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24094BO\"></sup>their eyes were heavy.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>So, leaving them again, he went away and prayed for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24095BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24095BP\"></sup>the third time, saying the same words again.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Then he came to the disciples and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Sleep and take your rest later on. See, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24096BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24096BQ\"></sup>the hour is at hand, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24096BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24096BR\"></sup>the Son of Man is betrayed into the hands of sinners.</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Rise, let us be going; see, my betrayer is at hand.”</span>",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24098BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24098BS\"></sup>While he was still speaking, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24098BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24098BT\"></sup>Judas came, one of the twelve, and with him a great crowd with swords and clubs, from the chief priests and the elders of the people.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>Now the betrayer had given them a sign, saying, “The one I will kiss is the man; seize him.”",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>And he came up to Jesus at once and said, “Greetings, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24100BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24100BU\"></sup>Rabbi!” And he kissed him.",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24101BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24101BV\"></sup>“Friend, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24101BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24101BW\"></sup>do what you came to do.”</span> Then they came up and laid hands on Jesus and seized him.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>And behold, one of those who were with Jesus stretched out his hand and drew his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24102BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24102BX\"></sup>sword and struck the servant of the high priest and cut off his ear.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>Then Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Put your sword back into its place. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24103BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24103BY\"></sup>all who take the sword will perish by the sword.</span>",
			"53": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24104BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24104BZ\"></sup>Do you think that I cannot appeal to my Father, and he will at once send me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24104CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24104CA\"></sup>more than twelve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24104CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24104CB\"></sup>legions of angels?</span>",
			"54": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24105CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24105CC\"></sup>But how then should the Scriptures be fulfilled, that it must be so?”</span>",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>At that hour Jesus said to the crowds, <span class=\"woj\">“Have you come out as against a robber, with swords and clubs to capture me? Day after day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24106CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24106CD\"></sup>I sat in the temple <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24106CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24106CE\"></sup>teaching, and you did not seize me.</span>",
			"56": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24107CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24107CF\"></sup>all this has taken place that the Scriptures of the prophets might be fulfilled.”</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24107CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24107CG\"></sup>Then all the disciples left him and fled.",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24108CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24108CH\"></sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24108CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24108CI\"></sup>those who had seized Jesus led him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24108CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24108CJ\"></sup>Caiaphas the high priest, where the scribes and the elders had gathered.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24109CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24109CK\"></sup>Peter was following him at a distance, as far as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24109CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24109CL\"></sup>the courtyard of the high priest, and going inside he sat with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24109CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24109CM\"></sup>the guards to see the end.",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>Now the chief priests and the whole council <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24110CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24110CN\"></sup>were seeking false testimony against Jesus that they might put him to death,",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>but they found none, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24111CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24111CO\"></sup>though many false witnesses came forward. At last <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24111CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24111CP\"></sup>two came forward",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>and said, “This man said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24112CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24112CQ\"></sup>‘I am able to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24112CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24112CR\"></sup>destroy the temple of God, and to rebuild it in three days.’”",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>And the high priest stood up and said, “Have you no answer to make? What is it that these men testify against you?”",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24114CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24114CS\"></sup>But Jesus remained silent. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24114CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24114CT\"></sup>And the high priest said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24114CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24114CU\"></sup>“I adjure you by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24114CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24114CV\"></sup>the living God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24114CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24114CW\"></sup>tell us if you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24114CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24114CX\"></sup>the Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24114CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24114CY\"></sup>the Son of God.”",
			"64": "<sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24115CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24115CZ\"></sup>“You have said so. But I tell you, from now on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24115DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24115DA\"></sup>you will see the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24115DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24115DB\"></sup>seated at the right hand of Power and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24115DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24115DC\"></sup>coming on the clouds of heaven.”</span>",
			"65": "<sup class=\"versenum\">65 </sup>Then the high priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24116DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24116DD\"></sup>tore his robes and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24116DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24116DE\"></sup>“He has uttered blasphemy. What further witnesses do we need? You have now heard his blasphemy.",
			"66": "<sup class=\"versenum\">66 </sup>What is your judgment?” They answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24117DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24117DF\"></sup>“He deserves death.”",
			"67": "<sup class=\"versenum\">67 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24118DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24118DG\"></sup>they spit in his face <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24118DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24118DH\"></sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24118DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24118DI\"></sup>struck him. And some slapped him,",
			"68": "<sup class=\"versenum\">68 </sup>saying, “Prophesy to us, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24119DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24119DJ\"></sup>Christ! Who is it that struck you?”",
			"69": "<sup class=\"versenum\">69 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24120DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24120DK\"></sup>Now Peter was sitting outside <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24120DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24120DL\"></sup>in the courtyard. And a servant girl came up to him and said, “You also were with Jesus the Galilean.”",
			"70": "<sup class=\"versenum\">70 </sup>But he denied it before them all, saying, “I do not know what you mean.”",
			"71": "<sup class=\"versenum\">71 </sup>And when he went out to the entrance, another servant girl saw him, and she said to the bystanders, “This man was with Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24122DM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DM&quot;&gt;DM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24122DM\"></sup>of Nazareth.”",
			"72": "<sup class=\"versenum\">72 </sup>And again he denied it with an oath: “I do not know the man.”",
			"73": "<sup class=\"versenum\">73 </sup>After a little while the bystanders came up and said to Peter, “Certainly you too are one of them, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24124DN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DN&quot;&gt;DN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24124DN\"></sup>your accent betrays you.”",
			"74": "<sup class=\"versenum\">74 </sup>Then he began to invoke a curse on himself and to swear, “I do not know the man.” And immediately the rooster crowed.",
			"75": "<sup class=\"versenum\">75 </sup>And Peter remembered the saying of Jesus, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24126DO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DO&quot;&gt;DO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24126DO\"></sup>“Before the rooster crows, you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24126DP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DP&quot;&gt;DP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24126DP\"></sup>deny me three times.”</span> And he went out and wept bitterly."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24127A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24127A\"></sup>When morning came, all the chief priests and the elders of the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24127B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24127B\"></sup>took counsel against Jesus to put him to death.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And they bound him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24128C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24128C\"></sup>led him away and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24128D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24128D\"></sup>delivered him over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24128E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24128E\"></sup>Pilate the governor.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24129F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24129F\"></sup>Judas, his betrayer, saw that Jesus was condemned, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24129G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24129G\"></sup>he changed his mind and brought back <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24129H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24129H\"></sup>the thirty pieces of silver to the chief priests and the elders,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>saying, “I have sinned by betraying innocent blood.” They said, “What is that to us? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24130I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24130I\"></sup>See to it yourself.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And throwing down the pieces of silver into the temple, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24131J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24131J\"></sup>he departed, and he went and hanged himself.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But the chief priests, taking the pieces of silver, said, “It is not lawful to put them into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24132K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24132K\"></sup>the treasury, since it is blood money.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So they took counsel and bought with them the potter's field as a burial place for strangers.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24134L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24134L\"></sup>that field has been called the Field of Blood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24134M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24134M\"></sup>to this day.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24135N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24135N\"></sup>Then was fulfilled what had been spoken by the prophet Jeremiah, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24135O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24135O\"></sup>“And they took the thirty pieces of silver, the price of him on whom a price had been set by some of the sons of Israel,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and they gave them for the potter's field, as the Lord directed me.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24137P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24137P\"></sup>Now Jesus stood before the governor, and the governor asked him, “Are you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24137Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24137Q\"></sup>the King of the Jews?” Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24137R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24137R\"></sup>“You have said so.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24138S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24138S\"></sup>But when he was accused by the chief priests and elders, he gave no answer.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then Pilate said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24139T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24139T\"></sup>“Do you not hear how many things they testify against you?”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But he gave him no answer, not even to a single charge, so that the governor was greatly amazed.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24141U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24141U\"></sup>Now at the feast the governor was accustomed to release for the crowd any one prisoner whom they wanted.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And they had then a notorious prisoner called Barabbas.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So when they had gathered, Pilate said to them, “Whom do you want me to release for you: Barabbas, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24143V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24143V\"></sup>Jesus who is called Christ?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For he knew that it was out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24144W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24144W\"></sup>of envy that they had delivered him up.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Besides, while he was sitting on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24145X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24145X\"></sup>the judgment seat, his wife sent word to him, “Have nothing to do with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24145Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24145Y\"></sup>that righteous man, for I have suffered much because of him today <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24145Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24145Z\"></sup>in a dream.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now the chief priests and the elders persuaded the crowd to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24146AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24146AA\"></sup>ask for Barabbas and destroy Jesus.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The governor again said to them, “Which of the two do you want me to release for you?” And they said, “Barabbas.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Pilate said to them, “Then what shall I do with Jesus who is called Christ?” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24148AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24148AB\"></sup>They all said, “Let him be crucified!”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And he said, “Why? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24149AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24149AC\"></sup>What evil has he done?” But they shouted all the more, “Let him be crucified!”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So when Pilate saw that he was gaining nothing, but rather that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24150AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24150AD\"></sup>a riot was beginning, he took water and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24150AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24150AE\"></sup>washed his hands before the crowd, saying, “I am innocent of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24150AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24150AF\"></sup>this man's blood; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24150AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24150AG\"></sup>see to it yourselves.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And all the people answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24151AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24151AH\"></sup>“His blood be on us and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24151AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24151AI\"></sup>on our children!”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Then he released for them Barabbas, and having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24152AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24152AJ\"></sup>scourged Jesus, delivered him to be crucified.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24153AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24153AK\"></sup>Then the soldiers of the governor took Jesus into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24153AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24153AL\"></sup>governor's headquarters, and they gathered the whole <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24153AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24153AM\"></sup>battalion before him.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And they stripped him and put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24154AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24154AN\"></sup>a scarlet robe on him,",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>and twisting together a crown of thorns, they put it on his head and put a reed in his right hand. And kneeling before him, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24155AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24155AO\"></sup>mocked him, saying, “Hail, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24155AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24155AP\"></sup>King of the Jews!”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24156AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24156AQ\"></sup>they spit on him and took the reed and struck him on the head.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And when they had mocked him, they stripped him of the robe and put his own clothes on him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24157AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24157AR\"></sup>led him away to crucify him.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24158AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24158AS\"></sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24158AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24158AT\"></sup>As they went out, they found a man of Cyrene, Simon by name. They compelled this man to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24158AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24158AU\"></sup>carry his cross.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24159AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24159AV\"></sup>And when they came to a place called Golgotha (which means Place of a Skull),",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24160AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24160AW\"></sup>they offered him wine to drink, mixed with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24160AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24160AX\"></sup>gall, but when he tasted it, he would not drink it.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And when they had crucified him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24161AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24161AY\"></sup>they divided his garments among them by casting lots.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Then they sat down and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24162AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24162AZ\"></sup>kept watch over him there.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And over his head they put the charge against him, which read, “This is Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24163BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24163BA\"></sup>the King of the Jews.”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Then two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24164BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24164BB\"></sup>robbers were crucified with him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24164BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24164BC\"></sup>one on the right and one on the left.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24165BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24165BD\"></sup>those who passed by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24165BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24165BE\"></sup>derided him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24165BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24165BF\"></sup>wagging their heads",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>and saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24166BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24166BG\"></sup>“You who would destroy the temple and rebuild it in three days, save yourself! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24166BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24166BH\"></sup>If you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24166BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24166BI\"></sup>the Son of God, come down from the cross.”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>So also the chief priests, with the scribes and elders, mocked him, saying,",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24168BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24168BJ\"></sup>“He saved others; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24168BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24168BK\"></sup>he cannot save himself. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24168BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24168BL\"></sup>He is the King of Israel; let him come down now from the cross, and we will believe in him.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24169BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24169BM\"></sup>He trusts in God; let God deliver him now, if he desires him. For he said, ‘I am the Son of God.’”",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24170BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24170BN\"></sup>And the robbers who were crucified with him also reviled him in the same way.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Now from the sixth hour there was darkness over all the land until the ninth hour.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>And about the ninth hour Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24172BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24172BO\"></sup>cried out with a loud voice, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24172BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24172BP\"></sup>“Eli, Eli, lema sabachthani?”</span> that is, <span class=\"woj\">“My God, my God, why have you forsaken me?”</span>",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>And some of the bystanders, hearing it, said, “This man is calling Elijah.”",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>And one of them at once ran and took a sponge, filled it with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24174BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24174BQ\"></sup>sour wine, and put it on a reed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24174BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24174BR\"></sup>gave it to him to drink.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>But the others said, “Wait, let us see whether Elijah will come to save him.”",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>And Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24176BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24176BS\"></sup>cried out again with a loud voice and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24176BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24176BT\"></sup>yielded up his spirit.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24177BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24177BU\"></sup>the curtain of the temple was torn in two, from top to bottom. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24177BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24177BV\"></sup>the earth shook, and the rocks were split.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>The tombs also were opened. And many bodies of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24178BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24178BW\"></sup>the saints <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24178BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24178BX\"></sup>who had fallen asleep were raised,",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>and coming out of the tombs after his resurrection they went into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24179BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24179BY\"></sup>the holy city and appeared to many.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24180BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24180BZ\"></sup>When the centurion and those who were with him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24180CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24180CA\"></sup>keeping watch over Jesus, saw the earthquake and what took place, they were filled with awe and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24180CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24180CB\"></sup>“Truly this was the Son of God!”",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>There were also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24181CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24181CC\"></sup>many women there, looking on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24181CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24181CD\"></sup>from a distance, who had followed Jesus from Galilee, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24181CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24181CE\"></sup>ministering to him,",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>among whom were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24182CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24182CF\"></sup>Mary Magdalene and Mary the mother of James and Joseph and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24182CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24182CG\"></sup>the mother of the sons of Zebedee.",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24183CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24183CH\"></sup>When it was evening, there came a rich man from Arimathea, named Joseph, who also was a disciple of Jesus.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>He went to Pilate and asked for the body of Jesus. Then Pilate ordered it to be given to him.",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>And Joseph took the body and wrapped it in a clean linen shroud",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24186CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24186CI\"></sup>laid it in his own new tomb, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24186CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24186CJ\"></sup>which he had cut in the rock. And he rolled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24186CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24186CK\"></sup>a great stone to the entrance of the tomb and went away.",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>Mary Magdalene and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24187CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24187CL\"></sup>the other Mary were there, sitting opposite the tomb.",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>The next day, that is, after the day of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24188CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24188CM\"></sup>Preparation, the chief priests and the Pharisees gathered before Pilate",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup>and said, “Sir, we remember how <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24189CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24189CN\"></sup>that impostor said, while he was still alive, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24189CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24189CO\"></sup>‘After three days I will rise.’",
			"64": "<sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup>Therefore order the tomb to be made secure until the third day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24190CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24190CP\"></sup>lest his disciples go and steal him away and tell the people, ‘He has risen from the dead,’ and the last fraud will be worse than the first.”",
			"65": "<sup class=\"versenum\">65 </sup>Pilate said to them, “You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24191CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24191CQ\"></sup>a guard of soldiers. Go, make it as secure as you can.”",
			"66": "<sup class=\"versenum\">66 </sup>So they went and made the tomb secure by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24192CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24192CR\"></sup>sealing the stone and setting a guard."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24193A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24193A\"></sup>Now after the Sabbath, toward the dawn of the first day of the week, Mary Magdalene and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24193B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24193B\"></sup>the other Mary went to see the tomb.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And behold, there was a great earthquake, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24194C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24194C\"></sup>an angel of the Lord descended from heaven and came and rolled back the stone and sat on it.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24195D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24195D\"></sup>His appearance was like lightning, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24195E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24195E\"></sup>his clothing white as snow.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And for fear of him the guards trembled and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24196F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24196F\"></sup>became like dead men.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But the angel said to the women, “Do not be afraid, for I know that you seek Jesus who was crucified.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He is not here, for he has risen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24198G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24198G\"></sup>as he said. Come, see the place where he lay.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then go quickly and tell his disciples that he has risen from the dead, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24199H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24199H\"></sup>he is going before you to Galilee; there you will see him. See, I have told you.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So they departed quickly from the tomb <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24200I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24200I\"></sup>with fear and great joy, and ran to tell his disciples.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And behold, Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24201J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24201J\"></sup>met them and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Greetings!”</span> And they came up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24201K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24201K\"></sup>took hold of his feet and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24201L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24201L\"></sup>worshiped him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Do not be afraid; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24202M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24202M\"></sup>go and tell <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24202N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24202N\"></sup>my brothers to go to Galilee, and there they will see me.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>While they were going, behold, some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24203O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24203O\"></sup>the guard went into the city and told the chief priests all that had taken place.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And when they had assembled with the elders and taken counsel, they gave a sufficient sum of money to the soldiers",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and said, “Tell people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24205P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24205P\"></sup>‘His disciples came by night and stole him away while we were asleep.’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And if this comes to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24206Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24206Q\"></sup>the governor's ears, we will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24206R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24206R\"></sup>satisfy him and keep you out of trouble.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So they took the money and did as they were directed. And this story has been spread among the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24207S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24207S\"></sup>to this day.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Now the eleven disciples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24208T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24208T\"></sup>went to Galilee, to the mountain to which Jesus had directed them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And when they saw him they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24209U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24209U\"></sup>worshiped him, but some doubted.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And Jesus came and said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24210V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24210V\"></sup>“All authority <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24210W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24210W\"></sup>in heaven and on earth has been given to me.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24211X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24211X\"></sup>Go therefore and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24211Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24211Y\"></sup>make disciples of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24211Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24211Z\"></sup>all nations, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24211AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24211AA\"></sup>baptizing them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24211AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24211AB\"></sup>in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24211AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24211AC\"></sup>the name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit,</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>teaching them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24212AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24212AD\"></sup>to observe all that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24212AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24212AE\"></sup>I have commanded you. And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24212AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24212AF\"></sup>I am with you always, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24212AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24212AG\"></sup>the end of the age.”</span>"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;